module: address-tracker-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(address-tracker-impl)
      +--rw timestamp-update-interval?   uint32
      +--rw observe-addresses-from?      string
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
         +--rw type?   service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: address-tracker
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw addresses* [id]
      +--rw id            uint64
      +--rw mac?          yang:mac-address
      +--rw ip?           inet:ip-address
      +--rw vlan?         ethernet:vlan-id
      +--rw first-seen?   int64
      +--rw last-seen?    int64
module: arp-handler-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(arp-handler-impl)
      +--rw arp-flow-table-id?               uint8
      +--rw arp-flow-priority?               uint16
      +--rw arp-flow-hard-timeout?           uint16
      +--rw arp-flow-idle-timeout?           uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-table-id?             uint8
      +--rw flood-flow-priority?             uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-hard-timeout?         uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-idle-timeout?         uint16
      +--rw flood-flow-installation-delay?   uint32
      +--rw is-proactive-flood-mode?         boolean
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
      |  +--rw type?   service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw rpc-registry
         +--rw type    service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: arp-packet
notifications:
   +---n arp-packet-received    
      +--ro packet-chain*
      |  +--ro (packet)?
      |     +--:(raw-packet)
      |        +--ro ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
      |        +--ro connection-cookie?   pprocessing:connection-cookie
      |        +--ro flow-cookie?         flow-type:flow-cookie
      |        +--ro table-id?            table-type:table-id
      |        +--ro packet-in-reason?    identityref
      |        +--ro match
      |        |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro metadata
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro tunnel
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro ethernet-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
      |        |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
      |        |  +--ro vlan-match
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |        |  +--ro ip-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |        |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |        |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |        |  +--ro icmpv4-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro icmpv6-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro pbb
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
      |        |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
      |        |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      |        +--ro payload-offset?      int32
      |        +--ro payload-length?      int32
      +--ro payload?        binary

      |  +--rw gve-timer?   uint32

      +--rw enable?                   empty
      +--rw description?              string

      +--rw enable?                   empty
      +--rw description?              string

module: brocade-arp
   +--rw hide-arp-holder
      o--rw system-max
      |  +--rw arp?   uint32
      +--rw arp-entry* [arp-ip-address]
         +--rw arp-ip-address            inet:ipv4-address
         +--rw mac-address-value?        mac-access-list:mac-address-type
         +--rw interfacename?            enumeration
         +--rw (interfacetype)?
            +--:(GigabitEthernet)
            |  +--rw GigabitEthernet?          interface:interface-type
            +--:(TenGigabitEthernet)
            |  +--rw TenGigabitEthernet?       interface:interface-type
            +--:(FortyGigabitEthernet)
            |  +--rw FortyGigabitEthernet?     interface:interface-type
            +--:(HundredGigabitEthernet)
            |  +--rw HundredGigabitEthernet?   interface:interface-type
            +--:(Ve)
               +--rw Ve?                       interface:vlan-type
augment /rbridge:rbridge-id:
   o--rw system-max
   |  +--rw arp?   uint32
   +--rw arp-entry* [arp-ip-address]
      +--rw arp-ip-address            inet:ipv4-address
      +--rw mac-address-value?        mac-access-list:mac-address-type
      +--rw interfacename?            enumeration
      +--rw (interfacetype)?
         +--:(GigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw GigabitEthernet?          interface:interface-type
         +--:(TenGigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw TenGigabitEthernet?       interface:interface-type
         +--:(FortyGigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw FortyGigabitEthernet?     interface:interface-type
         +--:(HundredGigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw HundredGigabitEthernet?   interface:interface-type
         +--:(Ve)
            +--rw Ve?                       interface:vlan-type
augment /rbridge:rbridge-id/vrf:vrf/vrf:address-family/vrf:ip/vrf:unicast:
   +--rw arp-entry* [arp-ip-address]
      +--rw arp-ip-address            inet:ipv4-address
      +--rw mac-address-value?        mac-access-list:mac-address-type
      +--rw interfacename?            enumeration
      +--rw (interfacetype)?
         +--:(GigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw GigabitEthernet?          interface:interface-type
         +--:(TenGigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw TenGigabitEthernet?       interface:interface-type
         +--:(FortyGigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw FortyGigabitEthernet?     interface:interface-type
         +--:(HundredGigabitEthernet)
         |  +--rw HundredGigabitEthernet?   interface:interface-type
         +--:(Ve)
            +--rw Ve?                       interface:vlan-type
rpcs:
   +---x get-arp    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w (input-type)?
      |     +--:(interface)
      |     |  +---w interface-type?   enumeration
      |     |  +---w interface-name?   union
      |     +--:(dynamic)
      |     |  +---w dynamic?          empty
      |     +--:(static)
      |     |  +---w static?           empty
      |     +--:(ip)
      |        +---w ip-address?       inet:ipv4-address
      +--ro output    
         +--ro arp-entry* [ip-address]
            +--ro ip-address        inet:ipv4-address
            +--ro mac-address?      mac-access-list:mac-address-type
            +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
            +--ro interface-name?   union
            +--ro is-resolved?      boolean
            +--ro age?              string
            +--ro entry-type?       enumeration

module: brocade-interface-ext
rpcs:
   +---x get-vlan-brief              
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w (request-type)?
   |  |     +--:(get-request)
   |  |     |  +---w vlan-id?             interface:vlan-type
   |  |     +--:(get-next-request)
   |  |        +---w last-rcvd-vlan-id?   interface:vlan-type
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro configured-vlans-count?      uint32
   |     +--ro provisioned-vlans-count?     uint32
   |     +--ro unprovisioned-vlans-count?   uint32
   |     +--ro vlan* [vlan-id]
   |     |  +--ro vlan-id       interface:vlan-type
   |     |  +--ro vlan-type?    enumeration
   |     |  +--ro vlan-name?    string
   |     |  +--ro vlan-state?   enumeration
   |     |  +--ro interface* [interface-type interface-name]
   |     |     +--ro interface-type    enumeration
   |     |     +--ro interface-name    union
   |     |     +--ro tag?              enumeration
   |     |     +--ro classification* [classification-type classification-value]
   |     |        +--ro classification-type     enumeration
   |     |        +--ro classification-value    string
   |     +--ro last-vlan-id?                interface:vlan-type
   |     +--ro has-more?                    boolean
   +---x get-interface-switchport    
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro switchport* [interface-type interface-name]
   |        +--ro interface-type            enumeration
   |        +--ro interface-name            union
   |        +--ro mode?                     interface:switchport-mode-type
   |        +--ro fcoe-port-enabled?        boolean
   |        +--ro ingress-filter-enabled?   boolean
   |        +--ro acceptable-frame-type?    enumeration
   |        +--ro default-vlan?             interface:vlan-type
   |        +--ro active-vlans
   |        |  +--ro vlanid*   interface:vlan-type
   |        +--ro inactive-vlans
   |           +--ro vlanid*   interface:vlan-type
   +---x get-ip-interface            
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w (request-type)?
   |  |     +--:(get-request)
   |  |        +---w interface-type?   enumeration
   |  |        +---w interface-name?   union
   |  |        +---w rbridge-id?       uint32
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro interface* [interface-type interface-name]
   |     |  +--ro interface-type         enumeration
   |     |  +--ro interface-name         union
   |     |  +--ro if-name?               string
   |     |  +--ro ip-address* [ipv4]
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv4         string
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-type?   enumeration
   |     |  |  +--ro broadcast?   string
   |     |  |  +--ro ip-mtu?      interface:mtu-type
   |     |  +--ro if-state?              enumeration
   |     |  +--ro line-protocol-state?   enumeration
   |     |  +--ro proxy-arp?             string
   |     |  +--ro vrf?                   string
   |     +--ro has-more?    boolean
   +---x get-interface-detail        
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w (request-type)?
   |  |     +--:(get-request)
   |  |     |  +---w interface-type?        enumeration
   |  |     |  +---w interface-name?        union
   |  |     +--:(get-next-request)
   |  |        +---w last-rcvd-interface
   |  |           +---w interface-type?   enumeration
   |  |           +---w interface-name?   union
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro interface* [interface-type interface-name]
   |     |  +--ro interface-type                  enumeration
   |     |  +--ro interface-name                  union
   |     |  +--ro ifindex?                        uint64
   |     |  +--ro mtu?                            interface:mtu-type
   |     |  +--ro ip-mtu?                         interface:mtu-type
   |     |  +--ro if-name?                        string
   |     |  +--ro if-state?                       enumeration
   |     |  +--ro line-protocol-state?            enumeration
   |     |  +--ro line-protocol-state-info?       string
   |     |  +--ro line-protocol-exception-info?   string
   |     |  +--ro hardware-type?                  enumeration
   |     |  +--ro logical-hardware-address?       yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--ro current-hardware-address?       yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--ro media-type?                     enumeration
   |     |  +--ro wavelength?                     uint32
   |     |  +--ro if-description?                 string
   |     |  +--ro actual-line-speed?              string
   |     |  +--ro configured-line-speed?          line-speed
   |     |  +--ro line-duplex-state?              enumeration
   |     |  +--ro flow-control?                   bits
   |     |  +--ro queuing-strategy?               enumeration
   |     |  +--ro port-role?                      enumeration
   |     |  +--ro port-mode?                      enumeration
   |     |  +--ro ifHCInOctets?                   yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCInUcastPkts?                yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCInMulticastPkts?            yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCInBroadcastPkts?            yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCInErrors?                   yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCOutOctets?                  yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCOutUcastPkts?               yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCOutMulticastPkts?           yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCOutBroadcastPkts?           yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro ifHCOutErrors?                  yang:counter64
   |     +--ro has-more?    boolean
   +---x get-media-detail            
      +---w input     
      |  +---w interface-type?   enumeration
      |  +---w interface-name?   union
      |  +---w rbridge-id?       common-def:rbridge-id-type
      +--ro output    
         +--ro interface* [interface-type interface-name]
            +--ro interface-type    enumeration
            +--ro interface-name    union
            +--ro (interface-identifier)?
               +--:(sfp)
               |  +--ro sfp
               |     +--ro speed?               line-speed

               |     +--ro media-form-factor?   enumeration
               |     +--ro wavelength?          string

               |     +--ro date-code?           string

               |     +--ro voltage?             decimal64
               |     +--ro current?             decimal64
               |     +--ro tx-power?            decimal64
               |     +--ro rx-power?            decimal64
               +--:(on-board)
               |  +--ro on-board
               |     +--ro speed?         line-speed
               |     +--ro connector?     enumeration
               |     +--ro encoding?      enumeration
               |     +--ro vendor-name?   string
               |     +--ro vendor-oui?    string
               |     +--ro vendor-pn?     string
               |     +--ro vendor-rev?    string
               +--:(gbic)

               |     +--ro vendor-name?   string

               |     +--ro vendor-rev?    string

               |     +--ro vendor-rev?    string
               +--:(xff)
               |  +--ro xff
               |     +--ro vendor-name?   string
               |     +--ro vendor-oui?    string
               |     +--ro vendor-pn?     string
               |     +--ro vendor-rev?    string
               +--:(xfpe)
               |  +--ro xfpe

module: brocade-interface
   +--rw interface
   |  +--rw gigabitethernet* [name]
   |  |  +--rw name                   interface-type
   |  |  +--ro ifindex?               uint64
   |  |  +--rw description?           string
   |  |  +--rw shutdown?              empty
   |  |  +--rw channel-group
   |  |  |  +--rw port-int?   portchannel-type
   |  |  |  +--rw mode?       po-mode
   |  |  |  +--rw type?       po-type
   |  |  +--rw mtu?                   mtu-type
   |  |  +--rw switchport-basic
   |  |  |  +--rw basic?   empty
   |  |  +--rw switchport
   |  |  |  +--rw mode
   |  |  |  |  +--rw vlan-mode?      l2-mode-type
   |  |  |  |  +--rw private-vlan
   |  |  |  |     +--rw private-vlan-trunk
   |  |  |  |     |  +--rw trunk-basic?         empty
   |  |  |  |     |  +--rw trunk-promiscuous?   empty
   |  |  |  |     |  +--rw trunk-host?          empty
   |  |  |  |     +--rw promiscuous?          empty
   |  |  |  |     +--rw host?                 empty
   |  |  |  +--rw port-security!
   |  |  |  |  +--rw port-sec-max?                uint32
   |  |  |  |  +--rw port-sec-violation?          port-sec-violation
   |  |  |  |  +--rw port-secutiry-mac-address* [mac-address port-sec-vlan]
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw mac-address      mac-address-type
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw port-sec-vlan    vlan-type
   |  |  |  |  +--rw sticky
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw sticky-flag?                 empty
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw port-secutiry-mac-address* [mac-address port-sec-vlan]
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw mac-address      mac-address-type
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw port-sec-vlan    vlan-type
   |  |  |  |  +--rw allowed-ouis* [oui]
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw oui    oui-type
   |  |  |  |  +--rw shutdown-time?               uint32
   |  |  |  +--rw access
   |  |  |  |  +--rw accessvlan?     vlan-type
   |  |  |  |  +--rw rspan-access
   |  |  |  |     +--rw rspan-access-vlan?   vlan-type
   |  |  |  +--rw access-mac-vlan-classification
   |  |  |  |  +--rw access
   |  |  |  |     +--rw vlan* [access-vlan-id access-mac-address]
   |  |  |  |        +--rw access-vlan-id        vlan-type
   |  |  |  |        +--rw access-mac-address    mac-address-type
   |  |  |  +--rw trunk-private-vlan-classification
   |  |  |  |  +--rw private-vlan
   |  |  |  |     +--rw trunk
   |  |  |  |        +--rw allowed
   |  |  |  |           +--rw vlan
   |  |  |  |              +--rw add* [trunk-vlan-id trunk-ctag-id]
   |  |  |  |              |  +--rw trunk-vlan-id    non-dot1q-vlan-type
   |  |  |  |              |  +--rw trunk-ctag-id    dot1q-vlan-type
   |  |  |  |              +--rw remove* [trunk-vlan-id trunk-ctag-id]
   |  |  |  |                 +--rw trunk-vlan-id    non-dot1q-vlan-type
   |  |  |  |                 +--rw trunk-ctag-id    dot1q-vlan-type
   |  |  |  +--rw access-mac-group-vlan-classification
   |  |  |  |  +--rw access
   |  |  |  |     +--rw vlan* [access-vlan-id access-mac-group]
   |  |  |  |        +--rw access-vlan-id      vlan-type
   |  |  |  |        +--rw access-mac-group    mac-group-id-type
   |  |  |  +--rw trunk
   |  |  |  |  +--rw allowed
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw vlan
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw all?      empty
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw none?     empty
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw add?      ui32-vlan-20k-range
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw except?   ui32-1k-vlan-range
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw remove?   ui32-1k-vlan-range
   |  |  |  |  |  x--rw vlanoper
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw vlan
   |  |  |  |  |  |     +--rw add?      ui32-vlan-range
   |  |  |  |  |  |     +--rw remove?   ui32-vlan-range
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw rspan-vlan
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw add-rspan-trunk-vlan?      ui32-1k-vlan-range
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw remove-rspan-trunk-vlan?   ui32-1k-vlan-range
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw trunk-rspan-vlan-classification
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw rspan-vlan

module: brocade-ip-access-list
   +--rw ip-acl
      +--rw ip
         +--rw access-list
            +--rw standard* [name]
            |  +--rw name               l3-acl-policy-name
            |  +--rw hide-ip-acl-std
            |     +--rw seq* [seq-id]
            |        +--rw seq-id              seq-id-std-ext
            |        +--rw action?             enumeration
            |        +--rw src-host-any-sip    union
            |        +--rw src-host-ip?        sip
            |        +--rw src-mask?           sip-mask
            |        +--rw count?              empty
            |        +--rw log?                empty
            +--rw extended* [name]
               +--rw name               l3-acl-policy-name
               +--rw hide-ip-acl-ext
                  +--rw seq* [seq-id]
                     +--rw seq-id                           seq-id-std-ext
                     +--rw action?                          enumeration
                     +--rw protocol-type                    union
                     +--rw src-host-any-sip                 union
                     +--rw src-host-ip?                     sip
                     +--rw src-mask?                        sip-mask
                     +--rw sport?                           enumeration
                     +--rw sport-number-eq-neq-tcp?         union
                     +--rw sport-number-lt-tcp?             union
                     +--rw sport-number-gt-tcp?             union
                     +--rw sport-number-eq-neq-udp?         union
                     +--rw sport-number-lt-udp?             union
                     +--rw sport-number-gt-udp?             union
                     +--rw sport-number-range-lower-tcp?    union
                     +--rw sport-number-range-lower-udp?    union
                     +--rw sport-number-range-higher-tcp?   union
                     +--rw sport-number-range-higher-udp?   union
                     +--rw dst-host-any-dip                 union
                     +--rw dst-host-ip?                     dip
                     +--rw dst-mask?                        dip-mask
                     +--rw dport?                           enumeration
                     +--rw dport-number-eq-neq-tcp?         union
                     +--rw dport-number-lt-tcp?             union
                     +--rw dport-number-gt-tcp?             union
                     +--rw dport-number-eq-neq-udp?         union
                     +--rw dport-number-lt-udp?             union
                     +--rw dport-number-gt-udp?             union
                     +--rw dport-number-range-lower-tcp?    union
                     +--rw dport-number-range-lower-udp?    union
                     +--rw dport-number-range-higher-tcp?   union
                     +--rw dport-number-range-higher-udp?   union
                     +--rw dscp?                            union
                     +--rw urg?                             empty
                     +--rw ack?                             empty
                     +--rw push?                            empty
                     +--rw fin?                             empty
                     +--rw rst?                             empty
                     +--rw sync?                            empty
                     +--rw vlan?                            interface:vlan-type
                     +--rw count?                           empty
                     +--rw log?                             empty

            +--rw hardware-address?   macAddr

   |  +--rw static-route-nh* [static-route-dest static-route-next-hop]
   |  |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  +--rw static-route-next-hop    inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  +--rw route-attributes
   |  |     +--rw metric?     uint32
   |  |     +--rw distance?   uint32
   |  |     +--rw tag?        uint32
   |  +--rw static-route-oif* [static-route-dest static-route-oif-type static-route-oif-name]
   |  |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  +--rw static-route-oif-type    enumeration
   |  |  +--rw static-route-oif-name    string
   |  |  +--rw route-attributes
   |  |     +--rw metric?     uint32
   |  |     +--rw distance?   uint32
   |  |     +--rw tag?        uint32
   |  +--rw link-local-static-route-nh* [link-local-static-route-dest link-local-nexthop link-local-route-oif-type link-local-route-oif-name]
   |  |  +--rw link-local-static-route-dest    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  +--rw link-local-nexthop              inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  +--rw link-local-route-oif-type       enumeration
   |  |  +--rw link-local-route-oif-name       string
   |  |  +--rw route-attributes
   |  |     +--rw metric?     uint32
   |  |     +--rw distance?   uint32
   |  |     +--rw tag?        uint32
   |  +--rw static-route-nh-vrf* [static-route-next-vrf-dest next-hop-vrf static-route-next-hop]
   |  |  +--rw static-route-next-vrf-dest    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  +--rw next-hop-vrf                  string
   |  |  +--rw static-route-next-hop         inet:ipv6-address
   |  +--rw link-local-static-route-nh-vrf* [static-route-next-vrf-dest next-hop-vrf link-local-next-hop link-local-route-oif-type link-local-route-oif-name]
   |  |  +--rw static-route-next-vrf-dest    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  +--rw next-hop-vrf                  string
   |  |  +--rw link-local-next-hop           inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  +--rw link-local-route-oif-type     enumeration
   |  |  +--rw link-local-route-oif-name     string
   |  +--rw static
   |     +--rw bfd
   |        +--rw bfd-ipv6-static-route* [bfd-ipv6-static-route-dest bfd-ipv6-static-route-src]
   |        |  +--rw bfd-ipv6-static-route-dest      inet:ipv6-address
   |        |  +--rw bfd-ipv6-static-route-src       inet:ipv6-address
   |        |  +--rw bfd-ipv6-interval-attributes
   |        |     +--rw interval?     uint16
   |        |     +--rw min-rx?       uint16
   |        |     +--rw multiplier?   uint8
   |        +--rw bfd-ipv6-link-local-static-route* [bfd-ipv6-link-local-dest bfd-ipv6-link-local-src bfd-interface-type bfd-interface-name]
   |        |  +--rw bfd-ipv6-link-local-dest        inet:ipv6-address
   |        |  +--rw bfd-ipv6-link-local-src         inet:ipv6-address
   |        |  +--rw bfd-interface-type              enumeration
   |        |  +--rw bfd-interface-name              string
   |        |  +--rw bfd-ipv6-interval-attributes
   |        |     +--rw interval?     uint16
   |        |     +--rw min-rx?       uint16
   |        |     +--rw multiplier?   uint8
   |        +--rw ipv6-holdover-interval?             uint8
   +--rw import
      +--rw routes* [src-vrf route-map]
         +--rw src-vrf      common-def:vrf-name
         +--rw route-map    common-def:name-string63

module: brocade-lag
   +--rw port-channel-redundancy-group* [group-id]
      +--rw group-id        po-redundancy-group-type
      +--rw port-channel* [name]
      |  +--rw name                   interface:portchannel-type
      |  +--rw port-channel-active?   empty
      +--rw activate?       empty
rpcs:
   +---x get-port-channel-detail         
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w last-aggregator-id?   interface:portchannel-type
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro lacp*
   |     |  +--ro aggregator-id?           interface:portchannel-type
   |     |  +--ro aggregator-type?         enumeration
   |     |  +--ro isvlag?                  boolean
   |     |  +--ro aggregator-mode?         enumeration
   |     |  +--ro admin-key?               lacp-key
   |     |  +--ro oper-key?                lacp-key
   |     |  +--ro actor-system-id?         yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--ro partner-system-id?       yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--ro system-priority?         uint32
   |     |  +--ro partner-oper-priority?   uint32
   |     |  +--ro rx-link-count?           uint64
   |     |  +--ro tx-link-count?           uint64
   |     |  +--ro individual-agg?          uint32
   |     |  +--ro ready-agg?               uint32
   |     |  +--ro partner-oper-key?        lacp-key
   |     |  +--ro aggr-member*
   |     |     +--ro rbridge-id?       uint32
   |     |     +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
   |     |     +--ro interface-name?   union
   |     |     +--ro actor-port?       uint64
   |     |     +--ro sync?             uint64
   |     +--ro has-more?   boolean
   +---x get-portchannel-info-by-intf    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w interface-type?   enumeration
      |  +---w interface-name?   union
      +--ro output    
         +--ro lacp
            +--ro interface-type?                        enumeration
            +--ro interface-name?                        union
            +--ro actor-port?                            uint64
            +--ro admin-key?                             lacp-key
            +--ro oper-key?                              lacp-key
            +--ro actor-system-id?                       yang:mac-address
            +--ro partner-system-id?                     yang:mac-address
            +--ro system-priority?                       uint32
            +--ro partner-oper-priority?                 uint32
            +--ro actor-priority?                        uint32
            +--ro receive-machine-state?                 enumeration
            +--ro periodic-transmission-machine-state?   enumeration
            +--ro mux-machine-state?                     enumeration
            +--ro admin-state?                           lacp-state
            +--ro oper-state?                            lacp-state
            +--ro partner-oper-state?                    lacp-state
            +--ro partner-oper-port?                     uint64
            +--ro actor-chip-number?                     uint32
            +--ro actor-max-deskew?                      uint32
            +--ro partner-chip-number?                   uint32
            +--ro partner-max-deskew?                    uint32
            +--ro actor-brcd-state?                      brcd-trunk-states
            +--ro partner-brcd-state?                    brcd-trunk-states

module: brocade-lldp-ext
rpcs:
   +---x get-lldp-neighbor-detail    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w (request-type)?
      |     +--:(get-request)
      |     |  +---w interface-type?      enumeration
      |     |  +---w interface-name?      union
      |     +--:(get-next-request)
      |     |  +---w last-rcvd-ifindex?   uint32
      |     +--:(get-rbridge-specific)
      |        +---w rbridge-id?          common-def:rbridge-id-type
      +--ro output    
         +--ro lldp-neighbor-detail* [local-interface-name remote-interface-name]
         |  +--ro local-interface-name         string
         |  +--ro local-interface-mac?         interface:mac-address-type
         |  +--ro local-interface-ifindex?     uint64
         |  +--ro remote-interface-name        string
         |  +--ro remote-interface-mac?        interface:mac-address-type
         |  +--ro remote-port-description?     string
         |  +--ro remote-chassis-id?           string
         |  +--ro remote-system-name?          string
         |  +--ro remote-system-description?   string
         |  +--ro dead-interval?               uint64
         |  +--ro remaining-life?              uint64
         |  +--ro lldp-pdu-transmitted?        yang:counter64
         |  +--ro lldp-pdu-received?           yang:counter64
         +--ro has-more?               boolean

module: brocade-mac-access-list
   +--rw mac
      +--rw access-list
         +--rw standard* [name]
         |  +--rw name                mac-acl-name
         |  +--rw hide-mac-acl-std
         |     +--rw seq* [seq-id]
         |        +--rw seq-id               uint64
         |        +--rw action?              enumeration
         |        +--rw source               union
         |        +--rw srchost?             mac-address-type
         |        +--rw src-mac-addr-mask?   src-dst-mac-address-mask-type
         |        +--rw count?               empty
         |        +--rw log?                 empty
         +--rw extended* [name]
            +--rw name                mac-acl-name
            +--rw hide-mac-acl-ext
               +--rw seq* [seq-id]
                  +--rw seq-id               uint64
                  +--rw action?              enumeration
                  +--rw source               union
                  +--rw srchost?             mac-address-type
                  +--rw src-mac-addr-mask?   src-dst-mac-address-mask-type
                  +--rw dst                  union
                  +--rw dsthost?             mac-address-type
                  +--rw dst-mac-addr-mask?   src-dst-mac-address-mask-type
                  +--rw ethertype?           union
                  +--rw vlan?                interface:vlan-type
                  +--rw count?               empty
                  +--rw log?                 empty

module: brocade-mac-address-table
   +--rw mac-address-table
   |  +--rw static* [mac-address forward interface-type interface-name vlan vlanid]
   |  |  +--rw mac-address       mac-access-list:mac-address-type
   |  |  +--rw forward           enumeration
   |  |  +--rw interface-type    enumeration
   |  |  +--rw interface-name    string
   |  |  +--rw vlan              enumeration
   |  |  +--rw vlanid            interface:vlan-type
   |  +--rw learning-mode?       enumeration
   |  +--rw aging-time
   |  |  +--rw conversational-time-out?   uint32
   |  |  +--rw legacy-time-out?           uint32
   |  +--rw mac-move
   |  |  +--rw mac-move-detect-enable?   empty
   |  |  +--rw mac-move-limit?           uint32
   |  +--rw consistency-check
   |     +--rw mac-consistency-check-suppress?   empty
   |     +--rw mac-consistency-check-interval?   uint32
   +--rw mac-group* [mac-group-id]
      +--rw mac-group-id       interface:mac-group-id-type
      +--rw mac-group-entry* [entry-address]
         +--rw entry-address    interface:mac-address-type
rpcs:
   +---x get-mac-address-table    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w (request-type)?
      |     +--:(get-request)
      |     |  +---w mac-address?                yang:mac-address
      |     +--:(get-next-request)
      |        +---w last-mac-address-details
      |           +---w last-mac-address?   yang:mac-address
      |           +---w last-vlan-id?       interface:vlan-type
      |           +---w last-mac-type?      enumeration
      +--ro output    
         +--ro mac-address-table* [vlanid mac-address]
         |  +--ro vlanid                  interface:vlan-type
         |  +--ro mac-address             yang:mac-address
         |  +--ro mac-type?               enumeration
         |  +--ro mac-state?              enumeration
         |  +--ro forwarding-interface*
         |     +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
         |     +--ro interface-name?   union
         +--ro has-more?            boolean

module: brocade-port-profile-ext
rpcs:
   +---x get-port-profile-for-intf    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w rbridge-id?                     uint32
   |  |  +---w (request-type)?
   |  |     +--:(get-request)
   |  |     |  +---w interface-type?                 enumeration
   |  |     |  +---w interface-name?                 union
   |  |     +--:(getnext-request)
   |  |        +---w last-received-interface-info
   |  |           +---w interface-type?   enumeration
   |  |           +---w interface-name?   union
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro interface*
   |     |  +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
   |     |  +--ro interface-name?   union
   |     |  +--ro port-profile*
   |     |     +--ro name?   common-def:name-string64
   |     +--ro has-more?    boolean
   +---x get-port-profile-status      
      +---w input     
      |  +---w rbridge-id?                        uint32
      |  +---w port-profile-name?                 common-def:name-string64
      |  +---w port-profile-status?               enumeration
      |  +---w (request-type)?
      |     +--:(getnext-request)
      |        +---w last-received-port-profile-info
      |           +---w profile-name?   common-def:name-string64
      |           +---w profile-mac?    inet:mac-address
      +--ro output    
         +--ro port-profile* [name]
            +--ro name               common-def:name-string64
            +--ro ppid?              uint32
            +--ro is-active?         boolean
            +--ro mac-association* [mac]
            |  +--ro mac                  inet:mac-address
            |  +--ro applied-interface
            |     +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
            |     +--ro interface-name?   union
            +--ro has-more?          boolean
module: brocade-port-profile
   +--rw port-profile* [name]
   |  +--rw name                           common-def:name-string128
   |  +--rw allow

   |  |     +--rw access-mac-group-vlan-classification

   |  |     +--rw trunk

   |  |        |        |  +--rw trunk-ctag-id    interface:dot1q-vlan-type

   |  |        |           +--rw trunk-vlan-id    interface:vlan-type
   |  |        |           +--rw trunk-ctag-id    interface:dot1q-vlan-type

   |  |  +--rw fcoeport
   |  |     +--rw fcoe-map-name?   string

   |  |  +--rw cee?   common-def:name-string32

   |  |     +--rw trust
   |  |     |  +--rw trust-cos?   empty

   |  |     +--rw cos-traffic-class?   common-def:name-string32
   |  |     +--rw flowcontrol

   |  |        |  +--rw tx?   enumeration
   |  |        |  +--rw rx?   enumeration

   |  |           +--rw pfc-rx     enumeration

         +--rw profile-name    port-profile-name-type

   |     |     +--rw metric?     uint32
   |     |     +--rw distance?   uint32
   |     |     +--rw tag?        uint32
   |     +--rw static-route-nh-vrf* [static-route-next-vrf-dest next-hop-vrf static-route-next-hop]
   |     |  +--rw static-route-next-vrf-dest    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  +--rw next-hop-vrf                  string
   |     |  +--rw static-route-next-hop         inet:ipv4-address
   |     +--rw static-route-oif* [static-route-dest static-route-oif-type static-route-oif-name]
   |     |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  +--rw static-route-oif-type    enumeration
   |     |  +--rw static-route-oif-name    string
   |     |  +--rw route-attributes

   |     |     +--rw distance?   uint32
   |     |     +--rw tag?        uint32
   |     +--rw static
   |        +--rw bfd
   |           +--rw bfd-static-route* [bfd-static-route-dest bfd-static-route-src]
   |           |  +--rw bfd-static-route-dest      inet:ipv4-address
   |           |  +--rw bfd-static-route-src       inet:ipv4-address
   |           |  +--rw bfd-interval-attributes
   |           |     +--rw interval?     uint16
   |           |     +--rw min-rx?       uint16
   |           |     +--rw multiplier?   uint8
   |           +--rw holdover-interval?   uint8
   +--rw import
      +--rw routes* [src-vrf route-map]
         +--rw src-vrf      common-def:vrf-name
         +--rw route-map    common-def:name-string63
augment /common-def:ip:
   +--rw rtm-config
      +--rw router-id?      inet:ipv4-address
      +--rw load-sharing?   uint32
      +--rw route
         +--rw static-route-nh* [static-route-dest static-route-next-hop]
         |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv4-prefix
         |  +--rw static-route-next-hop    inet:ipv4-address
         |  +--rw route-attributes
         |     +--rw metric?     uint32
         |     +--rw distance?   uint32
         |     +--rw tag?        uint32
         +--rw static-route-nh-vrf* [static-route-next-vrf-dest next-hop-vrf static-route-next-hop]
         |  +--rw static-route-next-vrf-dest    inet:ipv4-prefix
         |  +--rw next-hop-vrf                  string
         |  +--rw static-route-next-hop         inet:ipv4-address
         +--rw static-route-oif* [static-route-dest static-route-oif-type static-route-oif-name]
         |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv4-prefix
         |  +--rw static-route-oif-type    enumeration
         |  +--rw static-route-oif-name    string
         |  +--rw route-attributes
         |     +--rw metric?     uint32
         |     +--rw distance?   uint32
         |     +--rw tag?        uint32
         +--rw static
            +--rw bfd
               +--rw bfd-static-route* [bfd-static-route-dest bfd-static-route-src]
                  +--rw bfd-static-route-dest      inet:ipv4-address
                  +--rw bfd-static-route-src       inet:ipv4-address
                  +--rw bfd-interval-attributes
                     +--rw interval?     uint16
                     +--rw min-rx?       uint16
                     +--rw multiplier?   uint8

   +--rw ip
      +--rw route
      |  +--rw static-route-nh* [static-route-dest static-route-next-hop]
      |  |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  +--rw static-route-next-hop    inet:ipv4-address
      |  |  +--rw route-attributes
      |  |     +--rw metric?     uint32
      |  |     +--rw distance?   uint32
      |  |     +--rw tag?        uint32
      |  +--rw static-route-nh-vrf* [static-route-next-vrf-dest next-hop-vrf static-route-next-hop]
      |  |  +--rw static-route-next-vrf-dest    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  +--rw next-hop-vrf                  string
      |  |  +--rw static-route-next-hop         inet:ipv4-address
      |  +--rw static-route-oif* [static-route-dest static-route-oif-type static-route-oif-name]
      |  |  +--rw static-route-dest        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  +--rw static-route-oif-type    enumeration
      |  |  +--rw static-route-oif-name    string
      |  |  +--rw route-attributes
      |  |     +--rw metric?     uint32
      |  |     +--rw distance?   uint32
      |  |     +--rw tag?        uint32
      |  +--rw static
      |     +--rw bfd
      |        +--rw bfd-static-route* [bfd-static-route-dest bfd-static-route-src]
      |           +--rw bfd-static-route-dest      inet:ipv4-address
      |           +--rw bfd-static-route-src       inet:ipv4-address
      |           +--rw bfd-interval-attributes
      |              +--rw interval?     uint16
      |              +--rw min-rx?       uint16
      |              +--rw multiplier?   uint8
      +--rw import
         +--rw routes* [src-vrf route-map]
            +--rw src-vrf      common-def:vrf-name
            +--rw route-map    common-def:name-string63

module: brocade-trilloam
   +--rw trilloam
rpcs:
   +---x l2traceroute           
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w src-mac         mac:mac-address-type
   |  |  +---w dest-mac        mac:mac-address-type
   |  |  +---w vlan-id         interface:vlan-type
   |  |  +---w rbridge-id      common-def:rbridge-id-type
   |  |  +---w (protocolType)?
   |  |     +--:(IP)
   |  |     |  +---w src-ip          inet:ipv4-address
   |  |     |  +---w dest-ip         inet:ipv4-address
   |  |     |  +---w l4protocol      enumeration
   |  |     |  +---w l4-src-port     inet:port-number
   |  |     |  +---w l4-dest-port    inet:port-number
   |  |     +--:(FCoE)
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro session-id    uint32
   |     +--ro reason        string
   +---x l2traceroute-result    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w session-id    uint32
      +--ro output    
         +--ro l2-hop-results*
         |  +--ro l2-hop
         |     +--ro rbridge-id?      common-def:rbridge-id-type
         |     +--ro ingress
         |     |  +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
         |     |  +--ro interface-name?   union
         |     +--ro egress
         |     |  +--ro interface-type?   enumeration
         |     |  +--ro interface-name?   union
         |     +--ro roundtriptime?   common-def:time-interval-musec
         +--ro l2traceroutedone    boolean
         +--ro reason              string

      |  |     |  +--rw multiplier?   bfd-multiplier-type
      |  |     +--rw bfd-shutdown?   empty
      |  +--rw shutdown?     empty
      +--rw enable
      |  +--rw statistics
      |     +--rw stats-direction?   direction-type
      |     +--rw vlan-action?       enumeration
      |     +--rw vlan-list?         vfab-range-type
      +--rw monitor* [session]
      |  +--rw session            span:session-type
      |  +--rw direction?         direction-type
      |  +--rw remote-endpoint?   union
      |  +--rw vlan-leaf          enumeration
      |  +--rw vlan-add-remove?   enumeration
      |  +--rw vlan-range?        vfab-range-type
      +--rw sflow* [sflow-profile-name]
      |  +--rw sflow-profile-name       sflow:profile-name-type
      |  +--rw sflow-remote-endpoint?   union
      |  +--rw sflow-vlan-action        enumeration
      |  +--rw sflow-vlan-range?        vfab-range-type
      +--rw access-lists
      |  +--rw mac
      |  |  +--rw in
      |  |  |  +--rw mac-acl-in-name?   mac-access-list:mac-acl-name
      |  |  |  +--rw mac-acl-in-dir?    empty
      |  |  +--rw out
      |  |     +--rw mac-acl-out-name?   mac-access-list:mac-acl-name
      |  |     +--rw mac-acl-out-dir?    empty
      |  +--rw ipv4
      |  |  +--rw in
      |  |  |  +--rw ipv4-acl-in-name?   ip-access-list:l3-acl-policy-name
      |  |  |  +--rw ipv4-acl-in-dir?    empty
      |  |  +--rw out
      |  |     +--rw ipv4-acl-out-name?   ip-access-list:l3-acl-policy-name
      |  |     +--rw ipv4-acl-out-dir?    empty
      |  +--rw ipv6
      |     +--rw in
      |     |  +--rw ipv6-acl-in-name?   ip-access-list:l3-acl-policy-name
      |     |  +--rw ipv6-acl-in-dir?    empty
      |     +--rw out
      |        +--rw ipv6-acl-out-name?   ip-access-list:l3-acl-policy-name
      |        +--rw ipv6-acl-out-dir?    empty
      +--rw activate?       empty

      +--rw shutdown?     empty

module: brocade-vcs
   +--rw vcsmode
   |  +--rw vcs-mode            boolean
   |  +--rw vcs-cluster-mode    boolean
   +--rw local-node
   |  +--rw swbd-number    uint32
   +--rw vcs
      +--rw virtual
      |  +--rw ip
      |  |  +--rw address* [address]
      |  |     +--rw address    common-def:ipv4-address-prefix-type
      |  |     +--rw inband
      |  |        +--rw interface
      |  |           +--rw ve?   ve-type

      |        +--rw ipv6address    common-def:ipv6-address-prefix
      +--rw virtual-fabric
         +--rw vfab-enable?   empty
rpcs:
   +---x get-last-config-update-time               
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro last-config-update-time?   uint64
   +---x show-vcs                                  
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro principal-switch-wwn?              string
   |     +--ro co-ordinator-wwn?                  string
   |     +--ro vcs-cluster-type-info?             vcs-cluster-type
   |     +--ro vcs-guid?                          string
   |     +--ro virtual-ip-address?                string
   |     +--ro total-nodes-in-cluster?            uint16
   |     +--ro nodes-disconnected-from-cluster?   uint16
   |     +--ro cluster-generic-status?            string
   |     +--ro cluster-specific-status?           string
   |     +--ro vcs-nodes
   |        +--ro vcs-node-info*
   |           +--ro node-num?                     uint16
   |           +--ro node-serial-num?              string
   |           +--ro node-condition?               string
   |           +--ro node-status?                  string
   |           +--ro node-hw-sync-state?           node-hw-sync-state-type
   |           +--ro node-vcs-mode?                string
   |           +--ro node-vcs-id?                  uint16
   |           +--ro node-rbridge-id?              uint16
   |           +--ro node-is-principal?            boolean
   |           +--ro co-ordinator?                 boolean
   |           +--ro node-switch-mac?              yang:mac-address
   |           +--ro node-switch-wwn?              string
   |           +--ro switch-fcf-mac?               yang:mac-address
   |           +--ro node-internal-ip-address?     inet:ipv4-address
   |           +--ro node-public-ip-addresses*
   |           |  +--ro node-public-ip-address?   inet:ipv4-address
   |           +--ro node-public-ipv6-addresses*
   |           |  +--ro node-public-ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-address
   |           +--ro firmware-version?             string
   |           +--ro node-swbd-number?             int32
   |           +--ro node-switchname?              string
   |           +--ro node-switchtype?              string
   |           +--ro node-switch-subtype?          uint16
   |           +--ro node-switch-description?      string
   |           +--ro manufacturer-name?            string
   |           +--ro node-state?                   node-state-type
   |           +--ro node-fabric-state?            string
   +---x get-vcs-details                           
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro vcs-details
   |        +--ro principal-switch-wwn?   string
   |        +--ro co-ordinator-wwn?       string
   |        +--ro local-switch-wwn?       string
   |        +--ro node-vcs-mode?          boolean
   |        +--ro node-vcs-type?          vcs-cluster-type
   |        +--ro node-vcs-id?            uint32
   +---x vcs-rbridge-config                        
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w vcs-id?       uint16
   |     +---w rbridge-id?   uint16
   +---x vcs-rbridge-context                       
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w rbridge-id?   uint16
   +---x no-vcs-rbridge-context                    
   +---x get-last-config-update-time-for-xpaths    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w xpath-strings* [xpath-string]
      |     +---w xpath-string    string
      +--ro output    
         +--ro last-config-update-time-for-xpaths* [xpath-string]
            +--ro xpath-string               string
            +--ro last-config-update-time?   uint64

      |  |           +--rw encap?       enumeration

      |     +--rw ruleid       uint32

         +--rw tag
            +--rw native?   empty

      |  |     +--rw track-priority?   uint8
      |  +--rw advertisement-interval?   uint32
      |  +--rw enable?                   empty
      |  +--rw hold-time?                uint32
      |  +--rw preempt-mode?             empty
      |  +--rw priority?                 uint8
      |  +--rw description?              string
      +--rw vrrpv3e* [vrid]
         +--rw vrid                             vrid-type
         +--rw virtual-ip* [virtual-ipaddr]
         |  +--rw virtual-ipaddr    inet:ipv6-address
         +--rw track
         |  +--rw interface* [interface-type interface-name]
         |     +--rw interface-type    track-iftype
         |     +--rw interface-name    union
         |     +--rw track-priority?   uint8
         +--rw enable?                          empty
         +--rw hold-time?                       uint32
         +--rw preempt-mode?                    empty
         +--rw priority?                        uint8
         +--rw description?                     string
         +--rw advertise-backup?                empty
         +--rw nd-advertisement-timer?          uint32
         +--rw advertisement-interval-scale?    uint32
         +--rw backup-advertisement-interval?   uint32
         +--rw vrrpe-advertisement-interval?    uint32
         +--rw short-path-forwarding
            +--rw basic?             empty
            +--rw revert-priority?   uint8

      |  +--rw url?        vcenter-url

      |  +--rw password?   string
      +--rw activate?      empty
      +--rw interval?      uint32
      +--rw discovery
         +--rw ignore-delete-all-response
            +--rw ignore-value?   uint32
            +--rw always?         empty

         |     +--ro designated-port-id?          uint64
         |     +--ro port-priority?               uint32
         |     +--ro designated-bridge-id?        bridge-id-type
         |     +--ro port-hello-time?             uint32
         |     +--ro forward-transitions-count?   uint32
         |     +--ro received-stp-type?           stp-type
         |     +--ro transmitted-stp-type?        stp-type
         |     +--ro edge-port?                   on-off-type
         |     +--ro auto-edge?                   yes-no-type
         |     +--ro admin-edge?                  yes-no-type
         |     +--ro edge-delay?                  uint32
         |     +--ro configured-root-guard?       on-off-type
         |     +--ro oper-root-guard?             on-off-type
         |     +--ro boundary-port?               yes-no-type
         |     +--ro oper-bpdu-guard?             on-off-type
         |     +--ro oper-bpdu-filter?            on-off-type
         |     +--ro link-type?                   stp-link-type
         |     +--ro rx-bpdu-count?               uint64
         |     +--ro tx-bpdu-count?               uint64
         +--ro has-more?        boolean
         +--ro last-instance
            +--ro instance-id?   uint32

      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix

      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address

      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16

      |        +--ro payload-length?      int32
      +--ro payload?        binary

   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)

   |  |           |           |  +--rw set-dl-src-action

   |  |           |           +--:(group-action-case)

   |  |           |           |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
   |  |           |           |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)

   |  |           |           |     +--rw mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

   |  |           |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |  |           |           |  +--rw push-mpls-action

   |  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |              +--rw sw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(match)
   |  |           |  +--rw match-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(wildcards)
   |  |           |  +--rw wildcard-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield)
   |  |           |  +--rw write-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield-miss)
   |  |           |  +--rw write-setfield-miss
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield)
   |  |           |  +--rw apply-setfield
   |  |           |     +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
   |  |              +--rw apply-setfield-miss
   |  |                 +--rw set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |                    +--rw match-type    identityref
   |  |                    +--rw has-mask?     boolean
   |  +--rw flow* [id]
   |  |  +--rw id                flow-id
   |  |  +--rw match
   |  |  |  +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |  |  |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |  |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |  |  |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |  |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +--rw ethernet-match
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ethernet-source!

   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |  |  |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |  +--rw ip-match
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)

   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |  |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |  +--rw icmpv4-match
   |  |  |  |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |  |  |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +--rw protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |  |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |  |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |  |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8

   |  |  |  |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |  |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |  +--rw tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |     +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  +--rw instructions
   |  |  |  +--rw instruction* [order]
   |  |  |     +--rw order             int32
   |  |  |     +--rw (instruction)?
   |  |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |  |  |        |  +--rw go-to-table
   |  |  |        |     +--rw table_id?   uint8
   |  |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)
   |  |  |        |  +--rw write-metadata
   |  |  |        |     +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |     +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        +--:(write-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +--rw write-actions
   |  |  |        |     +--rw action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +--rw order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +--rw (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--rw output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--rw set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |  |  |        |           |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

   |  |  +--rw cookie?           flow-cookie
   |  |  +--rw table_id?         uint8
   |  |  +--rw container-name?   string
   |  |  +--rw cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |  |  +--rw buffer_id?        uint32
   |  |  +--rw out_port?         uint64
   |  |  +--rw out_group?        uint32
   |  |  +--rw flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +--rw flow-name?        string
   |  |  +--rw installHw?        boolean
   |  |  +--rw barrier?          boolean
   |  |  +--rw strict?           boolean
   |  +--rw flow-hash-id-map* [hash]
   |     +--rw hash       string
   |     +--rw flow-id?   flow-id
   +--rw group* [group-id]
   |  +--rw group-type?       group-types
   |  +--rw group-id          group-id
   |  +--rw group-name?       string
   |  +--rw container-name?   string
   |  +--rw barrier?          boolean
   |  +--rw buckets
   |     +--rw bucket* [bucket-id]
   |        +--rw bucket-id      bucket-id
   |        +--rw weight?        uint16
   |        +--rw watch_port?    uint32
   |        +--rw watch_group?   uint32
   |        +--rw action* [order]
   |           +--rw order                  int32
   |           +--rw (action)?
   |              +--:(output-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw output-action
   |              |     +--rw output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |              |     +--rw max-length?              uint16
   |              +--:(controller-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw controller-action
   |              |     +--rw max-length?   uint16
   |              +--:(set-field-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-field
   |              |     +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |              |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |              |     +--rw metadata
   |              |     |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
   |              |     |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
   |              |     +--rw tunnel
   |              |     |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
   |              |     |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-match
   |              |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
   |              |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
   |              |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
   |              |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
   |              |     +--rw vlan-match
   |              |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
   |              |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |              |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |              |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |              |     +--rw ip-match
   |              |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |              |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |              |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
   |              |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
   |              |     |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |              |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header
   |              |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |              |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |              |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
   |              |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!
   |              |     |  |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
   |              |     |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
   |              |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |              |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
   |              |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |              |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |              |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |              |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |              |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |              |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |              |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |              |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |              |     +--rw icmpv4-match
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |              |     +--rw icmpv6-match
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |              |     +--rw protocol-match-fields
   |              |     |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
   |              |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8
   |              |     |  +--rw pbb
   |              |     |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
   |              |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
   |              |     +--rw tcp-flag-match
   |              |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
   |              +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-queue-action
   |              |     +--rw queue?      string
   |              |     +--rw queue-id?   uint32
   |              +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-mpls-ttl-action
   |              |     +--rw mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |              +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-ttl-action
   |              |     +--rw nw-ttl?   uint8
   |              +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw push-pbb-action
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw pop-pbb-action
   |              +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw push-mpls-action
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |              |  +--rw dec-mpls-ttl
   |              +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |              |  +--rw dec-nw-ttl
   |              +--:(drop-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw drop-action
   |              +--:(flood-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw flood-action
   |              +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw flood-all-action
   |              +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw hw-path-action
   |              +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw loopback-action
   |              +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw pop-vlan-action
   |              +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw push-vlan-action
   |              |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
   |              |     +--rw tag?             int32
   |              |     +--rw pcp?             int32
   |              |     +--rw cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |              |     +--rw vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |              +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |              |  +--rw copy-ttl-out
   |              +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |              |  +--rw copy-ttl-in
   |              +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-dl-dst-action
   |              |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
   |              +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-dl-src-action
   |              |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
   |              +--:(group-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw group-action
   |              |     +--rw group?      string
   |              |     +--rw group-id?   uint32
   |              +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-dl-type-action
   |              |     +--rw dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |              +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-next-hop-action
   |              |     +--rw (address)?
   |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |              |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |              |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-dst-action
   |              |     +--rw (address)?
   |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |              |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |              |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-src-action
   |              |     +--rw (address)?
   |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |              |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |              |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |              +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-nw-tos-action
   |              |     +--rw tos?   int32
   |              +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-tp-dst-action
   |              |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
   |              +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-tp-src-action
   |              |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
   |              +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-vlan-cfi-action
   |              |     +--rw vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |              +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-vlan-id-action
   |              |     +--rw vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |              +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw set-vlan-pcp-action
   |              |     +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |              +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |              |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
   |              +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |                 +--rw sw-path-action
   +--rw meter* [meter-id]
   |  +--rw flags?                meter-flags
   |  +--rw meter-id              meter-id
   |  +--rw barrier?              boolean
   |  +--rw meter-name?           string
   |  +--rw container-name?       string
   |  +--rw meter-band-headers
   |     +--rw meter-band-header* [band-id]
   |        +--rw band-id                    band-id
   |        +--rw meter-band-types
   |        |  +--rw flags?   meter-band-type
   |        +--rw band-rate?                 uint32
   |        +--rw band-burst-size?           uint32
   |        +--rw (band-type)?
   |           +--:(drop)
   |           |  +--rw drop-rate?                 uint32
   |           |  +--rw drop-burst-size?           uint32
   |           +--:(dscp-remark)
   |           |  +--rw dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
   |           |  +--rw dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
   |           |  +--rw perc_level?                uint8
   |           +--:(experimenter)
   |              +--rw experimenter-rate?         uint32
   |              +--rw experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
   |              +--rw experimenter?              uint32
   +--rw ip-address?               inet:ip-address
   +--rw supported-match-types
   |  +--rw match-type* [match]
   |     +--rw support-state?   inv:support-type
   |     +--rw match            string
   +--rw supported-instructions
   |  +--rw instruction-type* [instruction]
   |     +--rw support-state?   inv:support-type
   |     +--rw instruction      string
   +--rw supported-actions
   |  +--rw action-type* [action]
   |     +--rw support-state?   inv:support-type
   |     +--rw action           string
   +--rw switch-features
      +--rw max_buffers?    uint32
      +--rw max_tables?     uint8
      +--rw capabilities*   identityref
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw port-number?           union
   +--rw hardware-address?      yang:mac-address
   +--rw configuration?         port-config
   +--rw advertised-features?   port-features
   +--rw name?                  string
   +--rw state
   |  +--rw link-down?   boolean
   |  +--rw blocked?     boolean
   |  +--rw live?        boolean
   +--rw current-feature?       port-features
   +--rw supported?             port-features
   +--rw peer-features?         port-features
   +--rw current-speed?         uint32
   +--rw maximum-speed?         uint32
   +--rw queue* [queue-id]
      +--rw queue-id    queue-id
      +--rw port?       uint32
      +--rw property?   uint16
augment /inv:node-updated:
   +---- manufacturer?             string
   +---- hardware?                 string
   +---- software?                 string
   +---- serial-number?            string
   +---- description?              string
   +---- table* [id]
   |  +---- id                uint8
   |  +---- table-features* [table-id]
   |  |  +---- table-id            uint8
   |  |  +---- name?               string
   |  |  +---- metadata-match?     uint64
   |  |  +---- metadata-write?     uint64
   |  |  +---- max-entries?        uint32

   |  |           |           |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
