   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-nw-tos-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- tos?   int32
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-tp-dst-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-id-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-pcp-action

   |  |           |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

   |  |           |           |              +---- sw-path-action

   |  |           |           |  +---- apply-actions
   |  |           |           |     +---- action* [order]
   |  |           |           |        +---- order                  int32
   |  |           |           |        +---- (action)?
   |  |           |           |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- output-action

   |  |           |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- controller-action

   |  |           |           |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- tunnel
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- ethernet-match
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp

   |  |           |           |           |     |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- (layer-3-match)?
   |  |           |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |           |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |           |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number

   |  |           |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number

   |  |           |           |           |  +---- pop-pbb-action
   |  |           |           |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- push-mpls-action
   |  |           |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |           |           |           |  +---- dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |           |           |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)

   |  |           |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id

   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     +---- icmpv4-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +---- icmpv6-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +---- protocol-match-fields
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- pbb
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     +---- tcp-flag-match
   |  |           |           |        +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-queue-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- queue?      string
   |  |           |           |     +---- queue-id?   uint32
   |  |           |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

   |  |           |           |  +---- push-vlan-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           |     +---- tag?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- pcp?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- cfi?             vlan-cfi

   |  |           |        +---- order                  int32
   |  |           |        +---- (action)?

   |  |           |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)

   |  |           |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id

   |  |           |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64

   |  |           |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8

   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header

   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16

   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |     +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |           |           |     +---- icmpv4-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +---- icmpv6-match
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |           |           |     +---- protocol-match-fields
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |           |           |     |  +---- pbb
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |           |           |     +---- tcp-flag-match
   |  |           |           |        +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-queue-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- queue?      string
   |  |           |           |     +---- queue-id?   uint32
   |  |           |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- pop-mpls-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |           |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- push-pbb-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- pop-pbb-action
   |  |           |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- push-mpls-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |           |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- dec-nw-ttl
   |  |           |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- drop-action
   |  |           |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- flood-action
   |  |           |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- flood-all-action
   |  |           |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- hw-path-action
   |  |           |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- loopback-action
   |  |           |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- pop-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- push-vlan-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |           |           |     +---- tag?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- pcp?             int32
   |  |           |           |     +---- cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- copy-ttl-out
   |  |           |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- copy-ttl-in
   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |           |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- group-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- group?      string
   |  |           |           |     +---- group-id?   uint32
   |  |           |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-dl-type-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |           |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-next-hop-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- (address)?
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |           |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |           |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |           |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |           |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-nw-tos-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- tos?   int32
   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-tp-dst-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-id-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |           |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |           |           |     +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |           |           |  +---- strip-vlan-action
   |  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |           |              +---- sw-path-action
   |  |           +--:(match)
   |  |           |  +---- match-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(wildcards)
   |  |           |  +---- wildcard-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield)
   |  |           |  +---- write-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(write-setfield-miss)
   |  |           |  +---- write-setfield-miss
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield)
   |  |           |  +---- apply-setfield
   |  |           |     +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |           |        +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |           |        +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  |           +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
   |  |              +---- apply-setfield-miss
   |  |                 +---- set-field-match* [match-type]
   |  |                    +---- match-type    identityref
   |  |                    +---- has-mask?     boolean
   |  +---- flow* [id]
   |     +---- id                flow-id
   |     +---- match
   |     |  +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  +---- metadata
   |     |  |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |  +---- tunnel
   |     |  |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  +---- ethernet-match
   |     |  |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +---- ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +---- ethernet-type!
   |     |  |     +---- type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |  +---- vlan-match
   |     |  |  +---- vlan-id!
   |     |  |  |  +---- vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  |  +---- vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  +---- ip-match
   |     |  |  +---- ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  +---- (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-label
   |     |  |  |  |  +---- ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |     |  |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!

   |     |  |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |  |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |  |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |  +---- icmpv4-match
   |     |  |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |     |  |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8

   |     |  |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  |  +---- pbb
   |     |  |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |  |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |  +---- tcp-flag-match
   |     |     +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     +---- instructions
   |     |  +---- instruction* [order]
   |     |     +---- order             int32
   |     |     +---- (instruction)?
   |     |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |     |        |  +---- go-to-table
   |     |        |     +---- table_id?   uint8
   |     |        +--:(write-metadata-case)

   |     |        |     +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |        +--:(write-actions-case)

   |     |        |     +---- action* [order]
   |     |        |        +---- order                  int32
   |     |        |        +---- (action)?
   |     |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- output-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- controller-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-field
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- metadata
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-match

   |     |        |           |     +---- tcp-flag-match
   |     |        |           |        +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-queue-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- queue?      string
   |     |        |           |     +---- queue-id?   uint32
   |     |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- pop-mpls-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-mpls-ttl-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-nw-ttl-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- nw-ttl?   uint8
   |     |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- push-pbb-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- pop-pbb-action
   |     |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- push-mpls-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- dec-mpls-ttl
   |     |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- dec-nw-ttl
   |     |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- drop-action
   |     |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- flood-action
   |     |        |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- flood-all-action
   |     |        |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- hw-path-action
   |     |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- loopback-action
   |     |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- pop-vlan-action
   |     |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- push-vlan-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-type?   uint16
   |     |        |           |     +---- tag?             int32
   |     |        |           |     +---- pcp?             int32
   |     |        |           |     +---- cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |     |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- copy-ttl-out
   |     |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- copy-ttl-in
   |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-dl-dst-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- address?   yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-dl-src-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- address?   yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- group-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- group?      string
   |     |        |           |     +---- group-id?   uint32
   |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-dl-type-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |     |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-next-hop-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- (address)?
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |        |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |        |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-nw-dst-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- (address)?
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |        |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |        |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |        |           |        |  +---- ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |        |           |           +---- ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)

   |     |        |           |     +---- tos?   int32
   |     |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-tp-src-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- port?   inet:port-number
   |     |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

   |     |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |        |              +---- sw-path-action
   |     |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
   |     |        |  +---- apply-actions
   |     |        |     +---- action* [order]
   |     |        |        +---- order                  int32
   |     |        |        +---- (action)?
   |     |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- output-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?              uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- controller-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- max-length?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-field
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- metadata
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata?        uint64
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |        |           |     +---- tunnel
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |        |           |     +---- ethernet-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ethernet-source!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ethernet-destination!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ethernet-type!
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |        |           |     +---- vlan-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- vlan-id!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |        |           |     +---- ip-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |        |           |     +---- (layer-3-match)?
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-label
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- ipv6-ext-header
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     +---- icmpv4-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     +---- icmpv6-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     +---- protocol-match-fields
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- pbb
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     |        |           |     +---- tcp-flag-match
   |     |        |           |        +---- tcp-flag?   uint16
   |     |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |     |        |           |  +---- set-queue-action
   |     |        |           |     +---- queue?      string

   |     |        |           |     +---- in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |        |           |     +---- metadata

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- tunnel-mask?   uint64

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- ip-ecn?        uint8

   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- address    yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  |     +---- mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |        |           |     +---- (layer-4-match)?
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  |  +---- tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     |     +---- sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     |        |           |     +---- icmpv4-match
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |        |           |     |  +---- icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |     |        |           |     |     +---- pbb-mask?   uint32

module: flow-topology-discovery
rpcs:
   +---x solicit-refresh    
notifications:
   +---n link-discovered            
   |  +--ro source?        inv:node-connector-ref
   |  +--ro destination?   inv:node-connector-ref
   +---n link-overutilized          
   |  +--ro source?        inv:node-connector-ref
   |  +--ro destination?   inv:node-connector-ref
   +---n link-removed               
   |  +--ro source?        inv:node-connector-ref
   |  +--ro destination?   inv:node-connector-ref
   +---n link-utilization-normal    
      +--ro source?        inv:node-connector-ref
      +--ro destination?   inv:node-connector-ref
module: host-tracker-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(host-tracker-impl)
      +--rw topology-id?            string
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
         +--rw type?   service-type-ref
         +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
module: host-tracker-service
augment /topo:network-topology/topo:topology/topo:node:
   +--rw addresses* [id]
   |  +--rw id            uint64
   |  +--rw mac?          yang:mac-address
   |  +--rw ip?           inet:ip-address
   |  +--rw vlan?         ethernet:vlan-id
   |  +--rw first-seen?   int64
   |  +--rw last-seen?    int64
   +--rw id?                  host-id
   +--rw attachment-points* [tp-id]
      +--rw tp-id               tp-id
      +--ro tp-ref*             tp-ref
      +--rw corresponding-tp?   topo:tp-ref
      +--rw active?             boolean
module: ietf-netconf-acm
   +--rw nacm
      +--rw enable-nacm?              boolean
      +--rw read-default?             action-type
      +--rw write-default?            action-type
      +--rw exec-default?             action-type
      +--rw enable-external-groups?   boolean
      +--ro denied-operations         yang:zero-based-counter32
      +--ro denied-data-writes        yang:zero-based-counter32
      +--ro denied-notifications      yang:zero-based-counter32
      +--rw groups
      |  +--rw group* [name]
      |     +--rw name         group-name-type
      |     +--rw user-name*   user-name-type
      +--rw rule-list* [name]
         +--rw name     string
         +--rw group*   union
         +--rw rule* [name]
            +--rw name                 string
            +--rw module-name?         union
            +--rw (rule-type)?
            |  +--:(protocol-operation)
            |  |  +--rw rpc-name?            union
            |  +--:(notification)
            |  |  +--rw notification-name?   union
            |  +--:(data-node)
            |     +--rw path                 node-instance-identifier
            +--rw access-operations?   union
            +--rw action               action-type
            +--rw comment?             string
module: ietf-netconf-monitoring-extension
augment /ncm:netconf-state/ncm:sessions/ncm:session:
   +--ro session-identifier?   string
module: ietf-netconf-monitoring
   +--ro netconf-state
      +--ro capabilities
      |  +--ro capability*   inet:uri
      +--ro datastores
      |  +--ro datastore* [name]
      |     +--ro name     netconf-datastore-type
      |     +--ro locks!
      |        +--ro (lock-type)?
      |           +--:(global-lock)
      |           |  +--ro global-lock
      |           |     +--ro locked-by-session    uint32
      |           |     +--ro locked-time          yang:date-and-time
      |           +--:(partial-lock)
      |              +--ro partial-lock* [lock-id]
      |                 +--ro lock-id              uint32
      |                 +--ro locked-by-session    uint32
      |                 +--ro locked-time          yang:date-and-time
      |                 +--ro select*              yang:xpath1.0
      |                 +--ro locked-node*         instance-identifier
      +--ro schemas
      |  +--ro schema* [identifier version format]
      |     +--ro identifier    string
      |     +--ro version       string
      |     +--ro format        identityref
      |     +--ro namespace     inet:uri
      |     +--ro location*     union
      +--ro sessions
      |  +--ro session* [session-id]
      |     +--ro session-id           uint32
      |     +--ro transport            identityref
      |     +--ro username             string
      |     +--ro source-host?         inet:host
      |     +--ro login-time           yang:date-and-time
      |     +--ro in-rpcs?             yang:zero-based-counter32
      |     +--ro in-bad-rpcs?         yang:zero-based-counter32
      |     +--ro out-rpc-errors?      yang:zero-based-counter32
      |     +--ro out-notifications?   yang:zero-based-counter32
      +--ro statistics
         +--ro netconf-start-time?   yang:date-and-time
         +--ro in-bad-hellos?        yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro in-sessions?          yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro dropped-sessions?     yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro in-rpcs?              yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro in-bad-rpcs?          yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro out-rpc-errors?       yang:zero-based-counter32
         +--ro out-notifications?    yang:zero-based-counter32
rpcs:
   +---x get-schema    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w identifier    string
      |  +---w version?      string
      |  +---w format?       identityref
      +--ro output    
         +--ro data    
module: ietf-netconf-notifications
notifications:
   +---n netconf-config-change        
   |  +--ro changed-by
   |  |  +--ro (server-or-user)
   |  |     +--:(server)
   |  |     |  +--ro server?        empty
   |  |     +--:(by-user)
   |  |        +--ro username       string
   |  |        +--ro session-id     nc:session-id-or-zero-type
   |  |        +--ro source-host?   inet:ip-address
   |  +--ro datastore?    enumeration
   |  +--ro edit*
   |     +--ro target?      instance-identifier
   |     +--ro operation?   nc:edit-operation-type
   +---n netconf-capability-change    
   |  +--ro changed-by
   |  |  +--ro (server-or-user)
   |  |     +--:(server)
   |  |     |  +--ro server?        empty
   |  |     +--:(by-user)
   |  |        +--ro username       string
   |  |        +--ro session-id     nc:session-id-or-zero-type
   |  |        +--ro source-host?   inet:ip-address
   |  +--ro added-capability*      inet:uri
   |  +--ro deleted-capability*    inet:uri
   |  +--ro modified-capability*   inet:uri
   +---n netconf-session-start        
   |  +--ro username       string
   |  +--ro session-id     nc:session-id-or-zero-type
   |  +--ro source-host?   inet:ip-address
   +---n netconf-session-end          
   |  +--ro username              string
   |  +--ro session-id            nc:session-id-or-zero-type
   |  +--ro source-host?          inet:ip-address
   |  +--ro killed-by?            nc:session-id-type
   |  +--ro termination-reason    enumeration
   +---n netconf-confirmed-commit     
      +--ro username         string
      +--ro session-id       nc:session-id-or-zero-type
      +--ro source-host?     inet:ip-address
      +--ro confirm-event    enumeration
      +--ro timeout?         uint32
module: ietf-netconf-with-defaults
augment /nc:get-config/nc:input:
   +---- with-defaults?   with-defaults-mode
augment /nc:get/nc:input:
   +---- with-defaults?   with-defaults-mode
augment /nc:copy-config/nc:input:
   +---- with-defaults?   with-defaults-mode
module: ietf-netconf
rpcs:
   +---x get-config         
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w source
   |  |  |  +---w (config-source)
   |  |  |     +--:(candidate)
   |  |  |     |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
   |  |  |     +--:(running)
   |  |  |     |  +---w running?     empty
   |  |  |     +--:(startup)
   |  |  |        +---w startup?     empty {startup}?
   |  |  +---w filter    
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro data    
   +---x edit-config        
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w target
   |     |  +---w (config-target)
   |     |     +--:(candidate)
   |     |     |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
   |     |     +--:(running)
   |     |        +---w running?     empty {writable-running}?
   |     +---w default-operation?   enumeration
   |     +---w test-option?         enumeration {validate}?
   |     +---w error-option?        enumeration
   |     +---w (edit-content)
   |        +--:(config)
   |        |  +---w config               
   |        +--:(url)
   |           +---w url?                 inet:uri {url}?
   +---x copy-config        
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w target
   |     |  +---w (config-target)
   |     |     +--:(candidate)
   |     |     |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
   |     |     +--:(running)
   |     |     |  +---w running?     empty {writable-running}?
   |     |     +--:(startup)
   |     |     |  +---w startup?     empty {startup}?
   |     |     +--:(url)
   |     |        +---w url?         inet:uri {url}?
   |     +---w source
   |        +---w (config-source)
   |           +--:(candidate)
   |           |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
   |           +--:(running)
   |           |  +---w running?     empty
   |           +--:(startup)
   |           |  +---w startup?     empty {startup}?
   |           +--:(url)
   |           |  +---w url?         inet:uri {url}?
   |           +--:(config)
   |              +---w config       
   +---x delete-config      
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w target
   |        +---w (config-target)
   |           +--:(startup)
   |           |  +---w startup?   empty {startup}?
   |           +--:(url)
   |              +---w url?       inet:uri {url}?
   +---x lock               
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w target
   |        +---w (config-target)
   |           +--:(candidate)
   |           |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
   |           +--:(running)
   |           |  +---w running?     empty
   |           +--:(startup)
   |              +---w startup?     empty {startup}?
   +---x unlock             
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w target
   |        +---w (config-target)
   |           +--:(candidate)
   |           |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
   |           +--:(running)
   |           |  +---w running?     empty
   |           +--:(startup)
   |              +---w startup?     empty {startup}?
   +---x get                
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w filter    
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro data    
   +---x close-session      
   +---x kill-session       
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w session-id    session-id-type
   +---x commit              {candidate}?
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w confirmed?         empty {confirmed-commit}?
   |     +---w confirm-timeout?   uint32 {confirmed-commit}?
   |     +---w persist?           string {confirmed-commit}?
   |     +---w persist-id?        string {confirmed-commit}?
   +---x discard-changes     {candidate}?
   +---x cancel-commit       {confirmed-commit}?
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w persist-id?   string
   +---x validate            {validate}?
      +---w input     
         +---w source
            +---w (config-source)
               +--:(candidate)
               |  +---w candidate?   empty {candidate}?
               +--:(running)
               |  +---w running?     empty
               +--:(startup)
               |  +---w startup?     empty {startup}?
               +--:(url)
               |  +---w url?         inet:uri {url}?
               +--:(config)
                  +---w config       
module: ipv4-packet
notifications:
   +---n ipv4-packet-received    
      +--ro packet-chain*
      |  +--ro (packet)?
      |     +--:(raw-packet)
      |        +--ro ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
      |        +--ro connection-cookie?   pprocessing:connection-cookie
      |        +--ro flow-cookie?         flow-type:flow-cookie
      |        +--ro table-id?            table-type:table-id
      |        +--ro packet-in-reason?    identityref
      |        +--ro match
      |        |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |        |  +--ro metadata
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro tunnel
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
      |        |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |        |  +--ro ethernet-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
      |        |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
      |        |  +--ro vlan-match
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |        |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |        |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |        |  +--ro ip-match
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |        |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |        |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |        |  |  +--:(arp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
      |        |  |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
      |        |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |        |  +--ro (layer-4-match)?
      |        |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |        |  |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |        |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |        |  |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |        |  +--ro icmpv4-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro icmpv6-match
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |        |  +--ro protocol-match-fields
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
      |        |  |  +--ro pbb
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
      |        |  |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
      |        |  +--ro tcp-flag-match
      |        |     +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
      |        +--ro payload-offset?      int32
      |        +--ro payload-length?      int32
      +--ro payload?        binary

   +--:(netty-immediate-event-executor)
module: netty-timer

module: network-topology
   +--rw network-topology
      +--rw topology* [topology-id]
         +--rw topology-id          topology-id
         +--rw topology-types
         +--rw underlay-topology* [topology-ref]
         |  +--rw topology-ref    topology-ref
         +--rw node* [node-id]
         |  +--rw node-id              node-id
         |  +--rw supporting-node* [node-ref]
         |  |  +--rw node-ref    node-ref
         |  +--rw termination-point* [tp-id]
         |     +--rw tp-id     tp-id
         |     +--ro tp-ref*   tp-ref
         +--rw link* [link-id]
            +--rw link-id            link-id
            +--rw source
            |  +--rw source-node    node-ref
            |  +--rw source-tp?     tp-ref
            +--rw destination
            |  +--rw dest-node    node-ref
            |  +--rw dest-tp?     tp-ref
            +--rw supporting-link* [link-ref]
               +--rw link-ref    link-ref
module: network-topology

         +--rw topology-types
         +--rw underlay-topology* [topology-ref]
         |  +--rw topology-ref    topology-ref

         |  +--rw node-id              node-id
         |  +--rw supporting-node* [node-ref]
         |  |  +--rw node-ref    node-ref
         |  +--rw termination-point* [tp-id]
         |     +--rw tp-id     tp-id
         |     +--ro tp-ref*   tp-ref
         +--rw link* [link-id]
            +--rw link-id            link-id
            +--rw source
            |  +--rw source-node    node-ref
            |  +--rw source-tp?     tp-ref
            +--rw destination
            |  +--rw dest-node    node-ref
            |  +--rw dest-tp?     tp-ref

               +--rw link-ref    link-ref

            |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

            +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

            +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

            +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
            |  +--rw pop-pbb-action

            +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

            +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
            |  +--rw dec-nw-ttl
            +--:(drop-action-case)
            |  +--rw drop-action
            +--:(flood-action-case)

            +--:(flood-all-action-case)

            |  +--rw copy-ttl-in
            +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-dl-dst-action
            |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
            +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-dl-src-action

            +--:(group-action-case)

            +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)

            |     +--rw dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
            +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
            |  +--rw set-next-hop-action
            |     +--rw (address)?

            |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
            |        +--:(ipv6)
            |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix

         +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:table:
   +--rw aggregate-flow-statistics
      +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
      +--rw flow-count?     yang:counter32

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!

   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |     |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |     |  |           +--ro meter
   |     |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |     |  +--ro priority?         uint16
   |     |  +--ro idle-timeout?     uint16
   |     |  +--ro hard-timeout?     uint16
   |     |  +--ro cookie?           flow-cookie
   |     |  +--ro table_id?         uint8
   |     |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |     |  +--ro cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |     |  +--ro buffer_id?        uint32
   |     |  +--ro out_port?         uint64
   |     |  +--ro out_group?        uint32
   |     |  +--ro flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |     |  +--ro flow-name?        string
   |     |  +--ro installHw?        boolean
   |     |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |     |  +--ro strict?           boolean
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |     +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |     +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id

   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?       node-ref
   |  |  +---w table-id?   table-types:table-id
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro flow-and-statistics-map-list* [flow-id]
   |     |  +--ro flow-id           flow-id
   |     |  +--ro match
   |     |  |  +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |  +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  |  |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |     |  |  |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |  |  +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |  |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |  +--ro ip-match
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |  +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)

   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |     |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |     |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |     |  |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
   |     |  |        |  +--ro apply-actions
   |     |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |     |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |     |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |     |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro controller-action
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |     |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-match

   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |     |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
