   |  |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(clear-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +--ro clear-actions
   |  |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--ro pbb
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
   |  |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro drop-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro flood-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro flood-all-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro loopback-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro group-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro group?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +--ro meter
   |  |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +--ro priority?         uint16
   |  |  +--ro idle-timeout?     uint16
   |  |  +--ro hard-timeout?     uint16
   |  |  +--ro cookie?           flow-cookie
   |  |  +--ro table_id?         uint8
   |  |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |  |  +--ro cookie_mask?      flow-cookie
   |  |  +--ro buffer_id?        uint32
   |  |  +--ro out_port?         uint64
   |  |  +--ro out_group?        uint32
   |  |  +--ro flags?            flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +--ro flow-name?        string
   |  |  +--ro installHw?        boolean
   |  |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |  |  +--ro strict?           boolean
   |  |  +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
   |  |  +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
   |  |  +--ro duration
   |  |     +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |  |     +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |  +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id
   +---n aggregate-flow-statistics-update    
      +--ro id?               node-id
      +--ro node-connector* [id]
      |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
      +--ro packet-count?     yang:counter64
      +--ro byte-count?       yang:counter64
      +--ro flow-count?       yang:counter32
      +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
      +--ro moreReplies?      boolean
module: opendaylight-flow-table-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:table:
   +--rw flow-table-statistics
      +--rw active-flows?        yang:counter32
      +--rw packets-looked-up?   yang:counter64
      +--rw packets-matched?     yang:counter64
rpcs:
   +---x get-flow-tables-statistics    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w node?   node-ref
      +--ro output    
         +--ro flow-table-and-statistics-map* [table-id]
         |  +--ro table-id             table-types:table-id
         |  +--ro active-flows?        yang:counter32
         |  +--ro packets-looked-up?   yang:counter64
         |  +--ro packets-matched?     yang:counter64
         +--ro transaction-id?                  transaction-id
notifications:
   +---n flow-table-statistics-update    
      +--ro id?                              node-id
      +--ro node-connector* [id]
      |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
      +--ro flow-table-and-statistics-map* [table-id]
      |  +--ro table-id             table-types:table-id
      |  +--ro active-flows?        yang:counter32
      |  +--ro packets-looked-up?   yang:counter64
      |  +--ro packets-matched?     yang:counter64
      +--ro transaction-id?                  transaction-id
      +--ro moreReplies?                     boolean
module: opendaylight-group-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/fni:group:
   +--rw group-statistics
      +--rw group-id?       group-id
      +--rw ref-count?      yang:counter32
      +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
      +--rw duration
      |  +--rw second?       yang:counter32
      |  +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
      +--rw buckets
         +--rw bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
            +--rw bucket-id       bucket-id
            +--rw packet-count?   yang:counter64
            +--rw byte-count?     yang:counter64
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/fni:group:
   +--rw group-desc
      +--rw group-type?       group-types
      +--rw group-id?         group-id
      +--rw group-name?       string
      +--rw container-name?   string
      +--rw barrier?          boolean
      +--rw buckets
         +--rw bucket* [bucket-id]
            +--rw bucket-id      bucket-id
            +--rw weight?        uint16
            +--rw watch_port?    uint32
            +--rw watch_group?   uint32
            +--rw action* [order]
               +--rw order                  int32
               +--rw (action)?
                  +--:(output-action-case)
                  |  +--rw output-action
                  |     +--rw output-node-connector?   inet:uri
                  |     +--rw max-length?              uint16
                  +--:(controller-action-case)
                  |  +--rw controller-action
                  |     +--rw max-length?   uint16
                  +--:(set-field-case)
                  |  +--rw set-field
                  |     +--rw in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
                  |     +--rw in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
                  |     +--rw metadata
                  |     |  +--rw metadata?        uint64
                  |     |  +--rw metadata-mask?   uint64
                  |     +--rw tunnel
                  |     |  +--rw tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |     |  +--rw tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |     +--rw ethernet-match
                  |     |  +--rw ethernet-source!
                  |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  +--rw ethernet-destination!
                  |     |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  +--rw ethernet-type!
                  |     |     +--rw type    l2t:ether-type
                  |     +--rw vlan-match
                  |     |  +--rw vlan-id!
                  |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |     |  |  +--rw vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |     |  +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |     +--rw ip-match
                  |     |  +--rw ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |     |  +--rw ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |     |  +--rw ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |     |  +--rw ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |     +--rw (layer-3-match)?
                  |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-label
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw ipv6-ext-header
                  |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
                  |     |  |     +--rw ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
                  |     |  +--:(arp-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-op?                         uint16
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-source-hardware-address!
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  |  +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |  +--rw arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |     |  |     +--rw address    yang:mac-address
                  |     |  |     +--rw mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
                  |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     |     +--rw tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |     +--rw (layer-4-match)?
                  |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |     |  |  +--rw udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |     |  |  +--rw tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |     |  |  +--rw tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
                  |     |     +--rw sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
                  |     |     +--rw sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
                  |     +--rw icmpv4-match
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv4-type?   uint8
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv4-code?   uint8
                  |     +--rw icmpv6-match
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv6-type?   uint8
                  |     |  +--rw icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |     +--rw protocol-match-fields
                  |     |  +--rw mpls-label?   uint32
                  |     |  +--rw mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |     |  +--rw mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |     |  +--rw pbb
                  |     |     +--rw pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |     |     +--rw pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |     +--rw tcp-flag-match
                  |        +--rw tcp-flag?   uint16
                  +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-queue-action
                  |     +--rw queue?      string
                  |     +--rw queue-id?   uint32
                  +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |  +--rw pop-mpls-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-mpls-ttl-action
                  |     +--rw mpls-ttl?   uint8
                  +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-ttl-action
                  |     +--rw nw-ttl?   uint8
                  +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
                  |  +--rw push-pbb-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |  +--rw pop-pbb-action
                  +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
                  |  +--rw push-mpls-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
                  |  +--rw dec-mpls-ttl
                  +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
                  |  +--rw dec-nw-ttl
                  +--:(drop-action-case)
                  |  +--rw drop-action
                  +--:(flood-action-case)
                  |  +--rw flood-action
                  +--:(flood-all-action-case)
                  |  +--rw flood-all-action
                  +--:(hw-path-action-case)
                  |  +--rw hw-path-action
                  +--:(loopback-action-case)
                  |  +--rw loopback-action
                  +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
                  |  +--rw pop-vlan-action
                  +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
                  |  +--rw push-vlan-action
                  |     +--rw ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |     +--rw tag?             int32
                  |     +--rw pcp?             int32
                  |     +--rw cfi?             vlan-cfi
                  |     +--rw vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
                  +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
                  |  +--rw copy-ttl-out
                  +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
                  |  +--rw copy-ttl-in
                  +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-dl-dst-action
                  |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
                  +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-dl-src-action
                  |     +--rw address?   yang:mac-address
                  +--:(group-action-case)
                  |  +--rw group-action
                  |     +--rw group?      string
                  |     +--rw group-id?   uint32
                  +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-dl-type-action
                  |     +--rw dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
                  +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-next-hop-action
                  |     +--rw (address)?
                  |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-dst-action
                  |     +--rw (address)?
                  |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-src-action
                  |     +--rw (address)?
                  |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |        |  +--rw ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           +--rw ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-nw-tos-action
                  |     +--rw tos?   int32
                  +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-tp-dst-action
                  |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
                  +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-tp-src-action
                  |     +--rw port?   inet:port-number
                  +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-vlan-cfi-action
                  |     +--rw vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
                  +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-vlan-id-action
                  |     +--rw vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
                  +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
                  |  +--rw set-vlan-pcp-action
                  |     +--rw vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
                  |  +--rw strip-vlan-action
                  +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                     +--rw sw-path-action
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node:
   +--rw group-features
      +--rw group-types-supported*          identityref
      +--rw group-capabilities-supported*   identityref
      +--rw max-groups*                     uint32
      +--rw actions*                        uint32
rpcs:
   +---x get-all-group-statistics    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro group-stats* [group-id]
   |     |  +--ro group-id        group-id
   |     |  +--ro ref-count?      yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro buckets
   |     |     +--ro bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
   |     |        +--ro bucket-id       bucket-id
   |     |        +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |        +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x get-group-statistics        
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?       node-ref
   |  |  +---w group-id?   group-types:group-id
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro group-stats* [group-id]
   |     |  +--ro group-id        group-id
   |     |  +--ro ref-count?      yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro buckets
   |     |     +--ro bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
   |     |        +--ro bucket-id       bucket-id
   |     |        +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |        +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x get-group-description       
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro group-desc-stats* [group-id]
   |     |  +--ro group-type?       group-types
   |     |  +--ro group-id          group-id
   |     |  +--ro group-name?       string
   |     |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |     |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |     |  +--ro buckets
   |     |     +--ro bucket* [bucket-id]
   |     |        +--ro bucket-id      bucket-id
   |     |        +--ro weight?        uint16
   |     |        +--ro watch_port?    uint32
   |     |        +--ro watch_group?   uint32
   |     |        +--ro action* [order]
   |     |           +--ro order                  int32
   |     |           +--ro (action)?
   |     |              +--:(output-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro output-action
   |     |              |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |     |              |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |     |              +--:(controller-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro controller-action
   |     |              |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |     |              +--:(set-field-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-field
   |     |              |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     |              |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     |              |     +--ro metadata
   |     |              |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |              |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     |              |     +--ro tunnel
   |     |              |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |              |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     |              |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |     |              |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |     |              |     +--ro vlan-match
   |     |              |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |              |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |              |     +--ro ip-match
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |              |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     |              |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |              |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |              |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |              |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |              |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |              |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |              |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |              |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!

   |     |              |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!

   |     |              |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |              |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |     |              |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number

   |     |              |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |              |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

   |     |              |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address

   |     |              |        +--:(ipv6)

   |     |              +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

   |     |              |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |     |              +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |     |              |     +--ro (address)?
   |     |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |     |              |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |     |              |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |              +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)

   |     |              |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |     |              +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |     |              |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |              +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |     |              |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |     |              +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |     |              |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |     |              |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |     |              +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)

   |     |              +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)

   |     |              |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     |              +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

   +---x get-group-features          
      +---w input     
      |  +---w node?   node-ref
      +--ro output    
         +--ro group-types-supported*          identityref
         +--ro group-capabilities-supported*   identityref
         +--ro max-groups*                     uint32
         +--ro actions*                        uint32
         +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id
notifications:
   +---n group-statistics-updated    
   |  +--ro id?               node-id
   |  +--ro node-connector* [id]
   |  |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
   |  +--ro group-stats* [group-id]
   |  |  +--ro group-id        group-id
   |  |  +--ro ref-count?      yang:counter32
   |  |  +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |  |  +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |  |  +--ro duration
   |  |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |  |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |  |  +--ro buckets
   |  |     +--ro bucket-counter* [bucket-id]
   |  |        +--ro bucket-id       bucket-id
   |  |        +--ro packet-count?   yang:counter64
   |  |        +--ro byte-count?     yang:counter64
   |  +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   |  +--ro moreReplies?      boolean
   +---n group-desc-stats-updated    
   |  +--ro id?                 node-id
   |  +--ro node-connector* [id]
   |  |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
   |  +--ro group-desc-stats* [group-id]
   |  |  +--ro group-type?       group-types
   |  |  +--ro group-id          group-id
   |  |  +--ro group-name?       string
   |  |  +--ro container-name?   string
   |  |  +--ro barrier?          boolean
   |  |  +--ro buckets
   |  |     +--ro bucket* [bucket-id]
   |  |        +--ro bucket-id      bucket-id
   |  |        +--ro weight?        uint16
   |  |        +--ro watch_port?    uint32
   |  |        +--ro watch_group?   uint32
   |  |        +--ro action* [order]
   |  |           +--ro order                  int32
   |  |           +--ro (action)?
   |  |              +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro output-action
   |  |              |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |              |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |  |              +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro controller-action
   |  |              |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-field
   |  |              |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |              |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |              |     +--ro metadata
   |  |              |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |              |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |              |     +--ro tunnel
   |  |              |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |              |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |              |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |  |              |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |              |     +--ro vlan-match
   |  |              |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |              |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |              |     +--ro ip-match
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |              |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |              |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |  |              |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |              |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |              |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |              |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |              |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |              |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |  |              |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |              |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |              |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |  |              |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |              |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |              |     +--ro icmpv6-match
   |  |              |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |              |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |              |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |  |              |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |              |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |              |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |              |     |  +--ro pbb
   |  |              |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |              |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |              |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |  |              |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-queue-action
   |  |              |     +--ro queue?      string
   |  |              |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
   |  |              +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
   |  |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |              |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |              |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |              +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro push-pbb-action
   |  |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
   |  |              +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro push-mpls-action
   |  |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |              +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
   |  |              +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro drop-action
   |  |              +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro flood-action
   |  |              +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro flood-all-action
   |  |              +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro hw-path-action
   |  |              +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro loopback-action
   |  |              +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
   |  |              +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro push-vlan-action
   |  |              |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              |     +--ro tag?             int32
   |  |              |     +--ro pcp?             int32
   |  |              |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |              |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |              +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
   |  |              +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
   |  |              +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
   |  |              |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |              +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
   |  |              |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |              +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro group-action
   |  |              |     +--ro group?      string
   |  |              |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
   |  |              +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
   |  |              |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |              +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
   |  |              |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |              |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |              |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
   |  |              |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |              |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |              |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |  |              |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |              |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |              |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |              |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |              +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |              |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |              +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |              |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |              +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |              |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |              +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |              |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |              +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |              |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |              +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |              |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |              +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |                 +--ro sw-path-action
   |  +--ro transaction-id?     transaction-id
   |  +--ro moreReplies?        boolean
   +---n group-features-updated      
      +--ro id?                             node-id
      +--ro node-connector* [id]
      |  +--ro id    node-connector-id
      +--ro group-types-supported*          identityref
      +--ro group-capabilities-supported*   identityref
      +--ro max-groups*                     uint32
      +--ro actions*                        uint32
      +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id
      +--ro moreReplies?                    boolean

         +--rw max-data-change-executor-pool-size?    uint16
         +--rw max-data-change-listener-queue-size?   uint16

         +--rw debug-transactions?                    boolean

module: opendaylight-inventory
   +--rw nodes
      +--rw node* [id]
         +--rw id                node-id
         +--rw node-connector* [id]
            +--rw id    node-connector-id
notifications:
   x---n node-updated              
   |  +--ro node-ref?         node-ref
   |  +--ro id?               node-id
   |  +--ro node-connector* [id]
   |     +--ro id    node-connector-id
   x---n node-connector-updated    
   |  +--ro node-connector-ref?   node-connector-ref
   |  +--ro id?                   node-connector-id
   x---n node-removed              
   |  +--ro node-ref?   node-ref
   x---n node-connector-removed    
      +--ro node-connector-ref?   node-connector-ref
module: opendaylight-meter-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:meter:
   +--rw meter-statistics
      +--rw meter-id?           meter-id
      +--rw flow-count?         yang:counter32
      +--rw packet-in-count?    yang:counter64
      +--rw byte-in-count?      yang:counter64
      +--rw duration
      |  +--rw second?       yang:counter32
      |  +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
      +--rw meter-band-stats
         +--rw band-stat* [band-id]
            +--rw band-id              band-id
            +--rw packet-band-count?   yang:counter64
            +--rw byte-band-count?     yang:counter64
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/flow-node:meter:
   +--rw meter-config-stats
      +--rw flags?                meter-flags
      +--rw meter-id?             meter-id
      +--rw barrier?              boolean
      +--rw meter-name?           string
      +--rw container-name?       string
      +--rw meter-band-headers
         +--rw meter-band-header* [band-id]
            +--rw band-id                    band-id
            +--rw meter-band-types
            |  +--rw flags?   meter-band-type
            +--rw band-rate?                 uint32
            +--rw band-burst-size?           uint32
            +--rw (band-type)?
               +--:(drop)
               |  +--rw drop-rate?                 uint32
               |  +--rw drop-burst-size?           uint32
               +--:(dscp-remark)
               |  +--rw dscp-remark-rate?          uint32
               |  +--rw dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
               |  +--rw perc_level?                uint8
               +--:(experimenter)
                  +--rw experimenter-rate?         uint32
                  +--rw experimenter-burst-size?   uint32
                  +--rw experimenter?              uint32
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node:
   +--rw meter-features
      +--rw max_meter?                      yang:counter32
      +--rw meter-band-supported*           identityref
      +--rw meter-capabilities-supported*   identityref
      +--rw max_bands?                      uint8
      +--rw max_color?                      uint8
rpcs:

   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro meter-stats* [meter-id]
   |     |  +--ro meter-id            meter-id
   |     |  +--ro flow-count?         yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro packet-in-count?    yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-in-count?      yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro meter-band-stats
   |     |     +--ro band-stat* [band-id]
   |     |        +--ro band-id              band-id
   |     |        +--ro packet-band-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |        +--ro byte-band-count?     yang:counter64
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x get-meter-statistics               
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?       node-ref
   |  |  +---w meter-id?   meter-types:meter-id
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro meter-stats* [meter-id]
   |     |  +--ro meter-id            meter-id
   |     |  +--ro flow-count?         yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro packet-in-count?    yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro byte-in-count?      yang:counter64
   |     |  +--ro duration
   |     |  |  +--ro second?       yang:counter32
   |     |  |  +--ro nanosecond?   yang:counter32
   |     |  +--ro meter-band-stats
   |     |     +--ro band-stat* [band-id]
   |     |        +--ro band-id              band-id
   |     |        +--ro packet-band-count?   yang:counter64
   |     |        +--ro byte-band-count?     yang:counter64
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x get-all-meter-config-statistics    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output

   |     |  +--ro meter-id              meter-id

   |     |  +--ro meter-name?           string
   |     |  +--ro container-name?       string
   |     |  +--ro meter-band-headers
   |     |     +--ro meter-band-header* [band-id]
   |     |        +--ro band-id                    band-id
   |     |        +--ro meter-band-types
   |     |        |  +--ro flags?   meter-band-type
   |     |        +--ro band-rate?                 uint32
   |     |        +--ro band-burst-size?           uint32
   |     |        +--ro (band-type)?
   |     |           +--:(drop)
   |     |           |  +--ro drop-rate?                 uint32
   |     |           |  +--ro drop-burst-size?           uint32
   |     |           +--:(dscp-remark)

   |     |           |  +--ro dscp-remark-burst-size?    uint32
   |     |           |  +--ro perc_level?                uint8

   |     |              +--ro experimenter?              uint32

   +---x get-meter-features

      |  +---w node?   node-ref

         +--ro meter-capabilities-supported*   identityref
         +--ro max_bands?                      uint8
         +--ro max_color?                      uint8
         +--ro transaction-id?                 transaction-id

module: opendaylight-port-statistics
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw flow-capable-node-connector-statistics
      +--rw packets
      |  +--rw received?      uint64
      |  +--rw transmitted?   uint64
      +--rw bytes
      |  +--rw received?      uint64
      |  +--rw transmitted?   uint64
      +--rw receive-drops?            uint64
      +--rw transmit-drops?           uint64
      +--rw receive-errors?           uint64
      +--rw transmit-errors?          uint64
      +--rw receive-frame-error?      uint64
      +--rw receive-over-run-error?   uint64
      +--rw receive-crc-error?        uint64
      +--rw collision-count?          uint64
      +--rw duration
         +--rw second?       yang:counter32
         +--rw nanosecond?   yang:counter32
rpcs:
   +---x get-all-node-connectors-statistics    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w node?   node-ref
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro node-connector-statistics-and-port-number-map* [node-connector-id]
   |     |  +--ro node-connector-id         inv:node-connector-id
   |     |  +--ro packets
   |     |  |  +--ro received?      uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro transmitted?   uint64
   |     |  +--ro bytes
   |     |  |  +--ro received?      uint64
   |     |  |  +--ro transmitted?   uint64
   |     |  +--ro receive-drops?            uint64
   |     |  +--ro transmit-drops?           uint64
   |     |  +--ro receive-errors?           uint64
   |     |  +--ro transmit-errors?          uint64
