   |     |     +---w oxm-class?         identityref
   |     |     +---w oxm-match-field?   identityref
   |     |     +---w has-mask?          boolean
   |     +---w instruction*
   |     |  +---w type?   identityref
   |     +---w flags-v10?      oft:flow-mod-flags-v10
   |     +---w match-v10
   |     |  +---w wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
   |     |  +---w nw-src-mask?   uint8
   |     |  +---w nw-dst-mask?   uint8
   |     |  +---w in-port?       uint16
   |     |  +---w dl-src?        yang:mac-address
   |     |  +---w dl-dst?        yang:mac-address
   |     |  +---w dl-vlan?       uint16
   |     |  +---w dl-vlan-pcp?   uint8
   |     |  +---w dl-type?       uint16
   |     |  +---w nw-tos?        uint8
   |     |  +---w nw-proto?      uint8
   |     |  +---w nw-src?        inet:ipv4-address
   |     |  +---w nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address
   |     |  +---w tp-src?        uint16
   |     |  +---w tp-dst?        uint16
   |     +---w action*
   |        +---w type?   identityref
   +---x group-mod            
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w version?        uint8
   |     +---w xid?            uint32
   |     +---w command?        oft:group-mod-command
   |     +---w type?           oft:group-type
   |     +---w group-id?       oft:group-id
   |     +---w buckets-list*
   |        +---w weight?        uint16
   |        +---w watch-port?    oft:port-number
   |        +---w watch-group?   uint32
   |        +---w action*
   |           +---w type?   identityref
   +---x port-mod             
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w version?         uint8
   |     +---w xid?             uint32
   |     +---w port-no?         oft:port-number
   |     +---w hw-address?      yang:mac-address
   |     +---w config?          oft:port-config
   |     +---w mask?            oft:port-config
   |     +---w advertise?       oft:port-features
   |     +---w config-v10?      oft:port-config-v10
   |     +---w mask-v10?        oft:port-config-v10
   |     +---w advertise-v10?   oft:port-features-v10
   +---x table-mod            
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w version?    uint8
   |     +---w xid?        uint32
   |     +---w table-id?   oft:table-id
   |     +---w config?     oft:table-config
   +---x multipart-request    
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w version?                            uint8
   |     +---w xid?                                uint32
   |     +---w type?                               oft:multipart-type
   |     +---w flags?                              oft:multipart-request-flags
   |     +---w (multipart-request-body)?
   |        +--:(multipart-request-desc-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-desc
   |        |     +---w empty?   empty
   |        +--:(multipart-request-flow-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-flow
   |        |     +---w table-id?      uint8
   |        |     +---w out-port?      uint32
   |        |     +---w out-group?     uint32
   |        |     +---w cookie?        uint64
   |        |     +---w cookie-mask?   uint64
   |        |     +---w match
   |        |     |  +---w type?            identityref
   |        |     |  +---w match-entries*
   |        |     |     +---w oxm-class?         identityref
   |        |     |     +---w oxm-match-field?   identityref
   |        |     |     +---w has-mask?          boolean
   |        |     +---w match-v10
   |        |        +---w wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
   |        |        +---w nw-src-mask?   uint8
   |        |        +---w nw-dst-mask?   uint8
   |        |        +---w in-port?       uint16
   |        |        +---w dl-src?        yang:mac-address
   |        |        +---w dl-dst?        yang:mac-address
   |        |        +---w dl-vlan?       uint16
   |        |        +---w dl-vlan-pcp?   uint8
   |        |        +---w dl-type?       uint16
   |        |        +---w nw-tos?        uint8
   |        |        +---w nw-proto?      uint8
   |        |        +---w nw-src?        inet:ipv4-address
   |        |        +---w nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address
   |        |        +---w tp-src?        uint16
   |        |        +---w tp-dst?        uint16
   |        +--:(multipart-request-aggregate-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-aggregate
   |        |     +---w table-id?      uint8
   |        |     +---w out-port?      uint32
   |        |     +---w out-group?     uint32
   |        |     +---w cookie?        uint64
   |        |     +---w cookie-mask?   uint64
   |        |     +---w match
   |        |     |  +---w type?            identityref
   |        |     |  +---w match-entries*
   |        |     |     +---w oxm-class?         identityref
   |        |     |     +---w oxm-match-field?   identityref
   |        |     |     +---w has-mask?          boolean
   |        |     +---w match-v10
   |        |        +---w wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
   |        |        +---w nw-src-mask?   uint8
   |        |        +---w nw-dst-mask?   uint8
   |        |        +---w in-port?       uint16
   |        |        +---w dl-src?        yang:mac-address
   |        |        +---w dl-dst?        yang:mac-address
   |        |        +---w dl-vlan?       uint16
   |        |        +---w dl-vlan-pcp?   uint8
   |        |        +---w dl-type?       uint16
   |        |        +---w nw-tos?        uint8
   |        |        +---w nw-proto?      uint8
   |        |        +---w nw-src?        inet:ipv4-address
   |        |        +---w nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address
   |        |        +---w tp-src?        uint16
   |        |        +---w tp-dst?        uint16
   |        +--:(multipart-request-table-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-table
   |        |     +---w empty?   empty
   |        +--:(multipart-request-port-stats-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-port-stats
   |        |     +---w port-no?   uint32
   |        +--:(multipart-request-queue-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-queue
   |        |     +---w port-no?    uint32
   |        |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |        +--:(multipart-request-group-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-group
   |        |     +---w group-id?   oft:group-id
   |        +--:(multipart-request-group-desc-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-group-desc
   |        |     +---w empty?   empty
   |        +--:(multipart-request-group-features-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-group-features
   |        |     +---w empty?   empty
   |        +--:(multipart-request-meter-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-meter
   |        |     +---w meter-id?   oft:meter-id
   |        +--:(multipart-request-meter-config-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-meter-config
   |        |     +---w meter-id?   oft:meter-id
   |        +--:(multipart-request-meter-features-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-meter-features
   |        |     +---w empty?   empty
   |        +--:(multipart-request-table-features-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-table-features
   |        |     +---w table-features*
   |        |        +---w table-id?                   uint8
   |        |        +---w name?                       string
   |        |        +---w metadata-match?             uint64
   |        |        +---w metadata-write?             uint64
   |        |        +---w config?                     oft:table-config
   |        |        +---w max-entries?                uint32
   |        |        +---w table-feature-properties*
   |        |           +---w type?   oft:table-features-prop-type
   |        +--:(multipart-request-port-desc-case)
   |        |  +---w multipart-request-port-desc
   |        |     +---w empty?   empty
   |        +--:(multipart-request-experimenter-case)
   |           +---w multipart-request-experimenter
   +---x barrier              
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w version?   uint8
   |  |  +---w xid?       uint32
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro version?   uint8
   |     +--ro xid?       uint32
   +---x get-queue-config     
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w version?   uint8
   |  |  +---w xid?       uint32
   |  |  +---w port?      oft:port-number
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro version?   uint8
   |     +--ro xid?       uint32
   |     +--ro port?      oft:port-number
   |     +--ro queues*
   |        +--ro queue-id?         oft:queue-id
   |        +--ro port?             oft:port-number
   |        +--ro queue-property*
   |           +--ro property?   oft:queue-properties
   +---x role-request         
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w version?         uint8
   |  |  +---w xid?             uint32
   |  |  +---w role?            oft:controller-role
   |  |  +---w generation-id?   uint64
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro version?         uint8
   |     +--ro xid?             uint32
   |     +--ro role?            oft:controller-role
   |     +--ro generation-id?   uint64
   +---x get-async            
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w version?   uint8
   |  |  +---w xid?       uint32
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro version?             uint8
   |     +--ro xid?                 uint32
   |     +--ro packet-in-mask*
   |     |  +--ro mask*   oft:packet-in-reason
   |     +--ro port-status-mask*
   |     |  +--ro mask*   oft:port-reason
   |     +--ro flow-removed-mask*
   |        +--ro mask*   oft:flow-removed-reason
   +---x set-async            
   |  +---w input     
   |     +---w version?             uint8
   |     +---w xid?                 uint32
   |     +---w packet-in-mask*
   |     |  +---w mask*   oft:packet-in-reason
   |     +---w port-status-mask*
   |     |  +---w mask*   oft:port-reason
   |     +---w flow-removed-mask*
   |        +---w mask*   oft:flow-removed-reason
   +---x meter-mod            
      +---w input     
         +---w version?    uint8
         +---w xid?        uint32
         +---w command?    oft:meter-mod-command
         +---w flags?      oft:meter-flags
         +---w meter-id?   oft:meter-id
         +---w bands*
            +---w (meter-band)?
               +--:(meter-band-drop-case)
               |  +---w meter-band-drop
               |     +---w type?         oft:meter-band-type
               |     +---w rate?         uint32
               |     +---w burst-size?   uint32
               +--:(meter-band-dscp-remark-case)
               |  +---w meter-band-dscp-remark
               |     +---w type?         oft:meter-band-type
               |     +---w rate?         uint32
               |     +---w burst-size?   uint32
               |     +---w prec-level?   uint8
               +--:(meter-band-experimenter-case)
                  +---w meter-band-experimenter
                     +---w type?         oft:meter-band-type
                     +---w rate?         uint32
                     +---w burst-size?   uint32
notifications:
   +---n hello-message              
   |  +--ro version?    uint8
   |  +--ro xid?        uint32
   |  +--ro elements*
   |     +--ro type?             oft:hello-element-type
   |     +--ro version-bitmap*   boolean
   +---n error-message              
   |  +--ro version?       uint8
   |  +--ro xid?           uint32
   |  +--ro type?          uint16
   |  +--ro code?          uint16
   |  +--ro type-string?   string
   |  +--ro code-string?   string
   |  +--ro data?          binary
   +---n echo-request-message       
   |  +--ro version?   uint8
   |  +--ro xid?       uint32
   |  +--ro data?      binary
   +---n experimenter-message       
   |  +--ro version?        uint8
   |  +--ro xid?            uint32
   |  +--ro experimenter?   oft:experimenter-id
   |  +--ro exp_type?       uint32
   +---n packet-in-message          
   |  +--ro version?     uint8
   |  +--ro xid?         uint32
   |  +--ro buffer-id?   uint32
   |  +--ro total-len?   uint16
   |  +--ro reason?      oft:packet-in-reason
   |  +--ro table-id?    oft:table-id
   |  +--ro cookie?      uint64
   |  +--ro match
   |  |  +--ro type?            identityref
   |  |  +--ro match-entries*
   |  |     +--ro oxm-class?         identityref
   |  |     +--ro oxm-match-field?   identityref
   |  |     +--ro has-mask?          boolean
   |  +--ro data?        binary
   |  +--ro in-port?     uint16
   +---n flow-removed-message       
   |  +--ro version?         uint8
   |  +--ro xid?             uint32
   |  +--ro cookie?          uint64
   |  +--ro priority?        uint16
   |  +--ro reason?          oft:flow-removed-reason
   |  +--ro table-id?        oft:table-id
   |  +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
   |  +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
   |  +--ro idle-timeout?    uint16
   |  +--ro hard-timeout?    uint16
   |  +--ro packet-count?    uint64
   |  +--ro byte-count?      uint64
   |  +--ro match
   |  |  +--ro type?            identityref
   |  |  +--ro match-entries*
   |  |     +--ro oxm-class?         identityref
   |  |     +--ro oxm-match-field?   identityref
   |  |     +--ro has-mask?          boolean
   |  +--ro match-v10
   |     +--ro wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
   |     +--ro nw-src-mask?   uint8
   |     +--ro nw-dst-mask?   uint8
   |     +--ro in-port?       uint16
   |     +--ro dl-src?        yang:mac-address
   |     +--ro dl-dst?        yang:mac-address
   |     +--ro dl-vlan?       uint16
   |     +--ro dl-vlan-pcp?   uint8
   |     +--ro dl-type?       uint16
   |     +--ro nw-tos?        uint8
   |     +--ro nw-proto?      uint8
   |     +--ro nw-src?        inet:ipv4-address
   |     +--ro nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address
   |     +--ro tp-src?        uint16
   |     +--ro tp-dst?        uint16
   +---n port-status-message        
   |  +--ro version?                   uint8
   |  +--ro xid?                       uint32
   |  +--ro port-no?                   uint32
   |  +--ro hw-addr?                   yang:mac-address
   |  +--ro name?                      string
   |  +--ro config?                    oft:port-config
   |  +--ro state?                     oft:port-state
   |  +--ro current-features?          oft:port-features
   |  +--ro advertised-features?       oft:port-features
   |  +--ro supported-features?        oft:port-features
   |  +--ro peer-features?             oft:port-features
   |  +--ro curr-speed?                uint32
   |  +--ro max-speed?                 uint32
   |  +--ro config-v10?                oft:port-config-v10
   |  +--ro state-v10?                 oft:port-state-v10
   |  +--ro current-features-v10?      oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro advertised-features-v10?   oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro supported-features-v10?    oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro peer-features-v10?         oft:port-features-v10
   |  +--ro reason?                    oft:port-reason
   +---n multipart-reply-message    
      +--ro version?                          uint8
      +--ro xid?                              uint32
      +--ro type?                             oft:multipart-type
      +--ro flags?                            oft:multipart-request-flags
      +--ro (multipart-reply-body)?
         +--:(multipart-reply-desc-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-desc
         |     +--ro mfr_desc?     string
         |     +--ro hw_desc?      string
         |     +--ro sw_desc?      string
         |     +--ro serial_num?   string
         |     +--ro dp_desc?      string
         +--:(multipart-reply-flow-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-flow
         |     +--ro flow-stats*
         |        +--ro table-id?        uint8
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         |        +--ro priority?        uint16
         |        +--ro idle-timeout?    uint16
         |        +--ro hard-timeout?    uint16
         |        +--ro flags?           oft:flow-mod-flags
         |        +--ro cookie?          uint64
         |        +--ro packet-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro byte-count?      uint64
         |        +--ro match
         |        |  +--ro type?            identityref
         |        |  +--ro match-entries*
         |        |     +--ro oxm-class?         identityref
         |        |     +--ro oxm-match-field?   identityref
         |        |     +--ro has-mask?          boolean
         |        +--ro instruction*
         |        |  +--ro type?   identityref
         |        +--ro match-v10
         |        |  +--ro wildcards?     oft:flow-wildcards-v10
         |        |  +--ro nw-src-mask?   uint8
         |        |  +--ro nw-dst-mask?   uint8
         |        |  +--ro in-port?       uint16
         |        |  +--ro dl-src?        yang:mac-address
         |        |  +--ro dl-dst?        yang:mac-address
         |        |  +--ro dl-vlan?       uint16
         |        |  +--ro dl-vlan-pcp?   uint8
         |        |  +--ro dl-type?       uint16
         |        |  +--ro nw-tos?        uint8
         |        |  +--ro nw-proto?      uint8
         |        |  +--ro nw-src?        inet:ipv4-address
         |        |  +--ro nw-dst?        inet:ipv4-address
         |        |  +--ro tp-src?        uint16
         |        |  +--ro tp-dst?        uint16
         |        +--ro action*
         |           +--ro type?   identityref
         +--:(multipart-reply-aggregate-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-aggregate
         |     +--ro packet-count?   uint64
         |     +--ro byte-count?     uint64
         |     +--ro flow-count?     uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-table-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-table
         |     +--ro table-stats*
         |        +--ro table-id?        uint8
         |        +--ro active-count?    uint32
         |        +--ro lookup-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro matched-count?   uint64
         |        +--ro name?            string
         |        +--ro wildcards?       oft:flow-wildcards-v10
         |        +--ro nw-src-mask?     uint8
         |        +--ro nw-dst-mask?     uint8
         |        +--ro max-entries?     uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-port-stats-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-port-stats
         |     +--ro port-stats*
         |        +--ro port-no?         uint32
         |        +--ro rx-packets?      uint64
         |        +--ro tx-packets?      uint64
         |        +--ro rx-bytes?        uint64
         |        +--ro tx-bytes?        uint64
         |        +--ro rx-dropped?      uint64
         |        +--ro tx-dropped?      uint64
         |        +--ro rx-errors?       uint64
         |        +--ro tx-errors?       uint64
         |        +--ro rx-frame-err?    uint64
         |        +--ro rx-over-err?     uint64
         |        +--ro rx-crc-err?      uint64
         |        +--ro collisions?      uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-queue-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-queue
         |     +--ro queue-stats*
         |        +--ro port-no?         uint32
         |        +--ro queue-id?        uint32
         |        +--ro tx-bytes?        uint64
         |        +--ro tx-packets?      uint64
         |        +--ro tx-errors?       uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-group-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-group
         |     +--ro group-stats*
         |        +--ro group-id?        oft:group-id
         |        +--ro ref-count?       uint32
         |        +--ro packet-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro byte-count?      uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?    uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?   uint32
         |        +--ro bucket-stats*
         |           +--ro packet-count?   uint64
         |           +--ro byte-count?     uint64
         +--:(multipart-reply-group-desc-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-group-desc
         |     +--ro group-desc*
         |        +--ro type?           oft:group-type
         |        +--ro group-id?       oft:group-id
         |        +--ro buckets-list*
         |           +--ro weight?        uint16
         |           +--ro watch-port?    oft:port-number
         |           +--ro watch-group?   uint32
         |           +--ro action*
         |              +--ro type?   identityref
         +--:(multipart-reply-group-features-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-group-features
         |     +--ro types?            oft:group-types
         |     +--ro capabilities?     oft:group-capabilities
         |     +--ro max_groups*       uint32
         |     +--ro actions-bitmap*   oft:action-type
         +--:(multipart-reply-meter-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-meter
         |     +--ro meter-stats*
         |        +--ro meter-id?           oft:meter-id
         |        +--ro flow-count?         uint32
         |        +--ro packet-in-count?    uint64
         |        +--ro byte-in-count?      uint64
         |        +--ro duration-sec?       uint32
         |        +--ro duration-nsec?      uint32
         |        +--ro meter-band-stats*
         |           +--ro packet-band-count?   uint64
         |           +--ro byte-band-count?     uint64
         +--:(multipart-reply-meter-config-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-meter-config
         |     +--ro meter-config*
         |        +--ro flags?      oft:meter-flags
         |        +--ro meter-id?   oft:meter-id
         |        +--ro bands*
         |           +--ro (meter-band)?
         |              +--:(meter-band-drop-case)
         |              |  +--ro meter-band-drop
         |              |     +--ro type?         oft:meter-band-type
         |              |     +--ro rate?         uint32
         |              |     +--ro burst-size?   uint32
         |              +--:(meter-band-dscp-remark-case)
         |              |  +--ro meter-band-dscp-remark
         |              |     +--ro type?         oft:meter-band-type
         |              |     +--ro rate?         uint32
         |              |     +--ro burst-size?   uint32
         |              |     +--ro prec-level?   uint8
         |              +--:(meter-band-experimenter-case)
         |                 +--ro meter-band-experimenter
         |                    +--ro type?         oft:meter-band-type
         |                    +--ro rate?         uint32
         |                    +--ro burst-size?   uint32
         +--:(multipart-reply-meter-features-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-meter-features
         |     +--ro max-meter?      uint32
         |     +--ro band-types?     oft:meter-band-type-bitmap
         |     +--ro capabilities?   oft:meter-flags
         |     +--ro max-bands?      uint8
         |     +--ro max-color?      uint8
         +--:(multipart-reply-table-features-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-table-features
         |     +--ro table-features*
         |        +--ro table-id?                   uint8
         |        +--ro name?                       string
         |        +--ro metadata-match?             binary
         |        +--ro metadata-write?             binary
         |        +--ro config?                     oft:table-config
         |        +--ro max-entries?                uint32
         |        +--ro table-feature-properties*
         |           +--ro type?   oft:table-features-prop-type
         +--:(multipart-reply-port-desc-case)
         |  +--ro multipart-reply-port-desc
         |     +--ro ports*
         |        +--ro port-no?                   uint32
         |        +--ro hw-addr?                   yang:mac-address
         |        +--ro name?                      string
         |        +--ro config?                    oft:port-config
         |        +--ro state?                     oft:port-state
         |        +--ro current-features?          oft:port-features
         |        +--ro advertised-features?       oft:port-features
         |        +--ro supported-features?        oft:port-features
         |        +--ro peer-features?             oft:port-features
         |        +--ro curr-speed?                uint32
         |        +--ro max-speed?                 uint32
         |        +--ro config-v10?                oft:port-config-v10
         |        +--ro state-v10?                 oft:port-state-v10
         |        +--ro current-features-v10?      oft:port-features-v10
         |        +--ro advertised-features-v10?   oft:port-features-v10
         |        +--ro supported-features-v10?    oft:port-features-v10
         |        +--ro peer-features-v10?         oft:port-features-v10
         +--:(multipart-reply-experimenter-case)
            +--ro multipart-reply-experimenter

module: packet-processing
rpcs:
   +---x transmit-packet    
      +---w input     
         +---w node?                node-ref
         +---w connection-cookie?   connection-cookie
         +---w egress?              inv:node-connector-ref
         +---w buffer-id?           uint32
         +---w ingress?             inv:node-connector-ref
         +---w payload?             binary
         +---w action* [order]
            +---w order                  int32
            +---w (action)?
               +--:(output-action-case)
               |  +---w output-action
               |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
               |     +---w max-length?              uint16
               +--:(controller-action-case)
               |  +---w controller-action
               |     +---w max-length?   uint16
               +--:(set-field-case)
               |  +---w set-field
               |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
               |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
               |     +---w metadata
               |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
               |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
               |     +---w tunnel
               |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
               |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
               |     +---w ethernet-match
               |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
               |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
               |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
               |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
               |     +---w vlan-match
               |     |  +---w vlan-id!
               |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
               |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
               |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
               |     +---w ip-match
               |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
               |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
               |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
               |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
               |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
               |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
               |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
               |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
               |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
               |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
               |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
               |     |  +--:(arp-match)
               |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
               |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
               |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
               |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
               |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
               |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
               |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
               |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
               |     |  +--:(udp-match)
               |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
               |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
               |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
               |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
               |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
               |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
               |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
               |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
               |     +---w icmpv4-match
               |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
               |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
               |     +---w icmpv6-match
               |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
               |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
               |     +---w protocol-match-fields
               |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
               |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
               |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
               |     |  +---w pbb
               |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
               |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
               |     +---w tcp-flag-match
               |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
               +--:(set-queue-action-case)
               |  +---w set-queue-action
               |     +---w queue?      string
               |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
               +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
               |  +---w pop-mpls-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
               |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
               |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
               +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
               |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
               +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
               |  +---w push-pbb-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
               |  +---w pop-pbb-action
               +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
               |  +---w push-mpls-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
               |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
               +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
               |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
               +--:(drop-action-case)
               |  +---w drop-action
               +--:(flood-action-case)
               |  +---w flood-action
               +--:(flood-all-action-case)
               |  +---w flood-all-action
               +--:(hw-path-action-case)
               |  +---w hw-path-action
               +--:(loopback-action-case)
               |  +---w loopback-action
               +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
               |  +---w pop-vlan-action
               +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
               |  +---w push-vlan-action
               |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
               |     +---w tag?             int32
               |     +---w pcp?             int32
               |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
               |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
               +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
               |  +---w copy-ttl-out
               +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
               |  +---w copy-ttl-in
               +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
               |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
               |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
               +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
               |  +---w set-dl-src-action
               |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
               +--:(group-action-case)
               |  +---w group-action
               |     +---w group?      string
               |     +---w group-id?   uint32
               +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
               |  +---w set-dl-type-action
               |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
               +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
               |  +---w set-next-hop-action
               |     +---w (address)?
               |        +--:(ipv4)
               |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |        +--:(ipv6)
               |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
               +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
               |     +---w (address)?
               |        +--:(ipv4)
               |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |        +--:(ipv6)
               |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
               +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-src-action
               |     +---w (address)?
               |        +--:(ipv4)
               |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
               |        +--:(ipv6)
               |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
               +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
               |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
               |     +---w tos?   int32
               +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
               |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
               |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
               +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
               |  +---w set-tp-src-action
               |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
               +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
               |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
               |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
               +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
               |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
               |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
               +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
               |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
               |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
               +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
               |  +---w strip-vlan-action
               +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                  +---w sw-path-action
notifications:

      +--ro connection-cookie?   connection-cookie

      |  +--ro ip-match

      |  |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header

      |  |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |  +--:(arp-match)

      |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |  |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |  +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |  +---w ip-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |  |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |  |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |  |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |  +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |     +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  +---w instructions
   |  |  |  +---w instruction* [order]
   |  |  |     +---w order             int32
   |  |  |     +---w (instruction)?
   |  |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w go-to-table
   |  |  |        |     +---w table_id?   uint8
   |  |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w write-metadata
   |  |  |        |     +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |     +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        +--:(write-actions-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w write-actions
   |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
   |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8

   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-mpls-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +---w meter
   |  |  |              +---w meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +---w priority?          uint16
   |  |  +---w idle-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w hard-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w cookie?            flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w table_id?          uint8
   |  |  +---w container-name?    string
   |  |  +---w cookie_mask?       flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w buffer_id?         uint32
   |  |  +---w out_port?          uint64
   |  |  +---w out_group?         uint32
   |  |  +---w flags?             flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +---w flow-name?         string
   |  |  +---w installHw?         boolean
   |  |  +---w barrier?           boolean
   |  |  +---w strict?            boolean
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x remove-flow    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  |  +---w flow-ref?          types:flow-ref
   |  |  +---w node?              node-ref
   |  |  +---w flow-table?        flow-table-ref
   |  |  +---w match
   |  |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |  +---w metadata
   |  |  |  |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |  |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +---w tunnel
   |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |  +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |  |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |  +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |  +---w ip-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |  |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |  |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |  +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |  |  |  +---w pbb
   |  |  |  |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |  |  |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |  |  +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |  |     +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |  +---w instructions
   |  |  |  +---w instruction* [order]
   |  |  |     +---w order             int32
   |  |  |     +---w (instruction)?
   |  |  |        +--:(go-to-table-case)
   |  |  |        |  +---w go-to-table
   |  |  |        |     +---w table_id?   uint8
   |  |  |        +--:(write-metadata-case)

   |  |  |        |     +---w metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
   |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header

   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields

   |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w pcp?             int32
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-out
   |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-in
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w group-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group?      string
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w group-id?   uint32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-dl-type-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-next-hop-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

   |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
   |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |  |           +---w meter
   |  |  |              +---w meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  |  +---w priority?          uint16
   |  |  +---w idle-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w hard-timeout?      uint16
   |  |  +---w cookie?            flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w table_id?          uint8
   |  |  +---w container-name?    string
   |  |  +---w cookie_mask?       flow-cookie
   |  |  +---w buffer_id?         uint32
   |  |  +---w out_port?          uint64
   |  |  +---w out_group?         uint32
   |  |  +---w flags?             flow-mod-flags
   |  |  +---w flow-name?         string
   |  |  +---w installHw?         boolean
   |  |  +---w barrier?           boolean
   |  |  +---w strict?            boolean
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x update-flow    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
      |  +---w flow-ref?          types:flow-ref
      |  +---w node?              node-ref
      |  +---w original-flow
      |  |  +---w match
      |  |  |  +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  |  +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

      |  |  |  |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |  |  |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |  +---w tunnel
      |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |  |  |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |  +---w ethernet-match
      |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-destination!

      |  |  |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |  |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |  |  |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |  |  +---w vlan-match
      |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id!

      |  |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |  |  |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

      |  |  |  |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  |  |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |  |  |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |  |  +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  +--:(ipv6-match)

      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

      |  |  |  |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label

      |  |  |  |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address

      |  |  |  |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |  |  |  +--:(arp-match)

      |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!

      |  |  |  |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

      |  |  |  |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |  +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  |  |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |  |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |  |  +---w instructions

      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-src-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (address)?
      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |  |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tos?   int32
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-tp-src-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w strip-vlan-action
      |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
      |  |  |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
      |  |  |        |  +---w apply-actions
      |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
      |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
      |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
      |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w controller-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16

      |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |  |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
