      |  |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |  |  |        |              +---w sw-path-action
      |  |  |        +--:(clear-actions-case)
      |  |  |        |  +---w clear-actions
      |  |  |        |     +---w action* [order]
      |  |  |        |        +---w order                  int32
      |  |  |        |        +---w (action)?
      |  |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w output-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-field
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w metadata

      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tunnel

      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!

      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-match

      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ip-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)

      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |  |        |           |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |  |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-queue-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
      |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w pop-mpls-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
      |  |  |        |           |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
      |  |  |        |           |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
      |  |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w tag?             int32

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id

      |  |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)

      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

      |  |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

      |  |  |        +--:(meter-case)
      |  |  |           +---w meter
      |  |  |              +---w meter-id?   meter:meter-id

      |  |  +---w idle-timeout?     uint16

      |     +---w match

      |     |  |  +--:(arp-match)

      |     |  |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

      |     |        |           |     +---w pcp?             int32
      |     |        |           |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
      |     |        |           |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
      |     |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-out
      |     |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w copy-ttl-in
      |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w set-dl-src-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w group-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w group?      string
      |     |        |           |     +---w group-id?   uint32
      |     |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w set-dl-type-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
      |     |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w set-next-hop-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w (address)?
      |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |     |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |     |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w (address)?
      |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
      |     |        |           |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
      |     |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |     |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)

      |     |        |           |     +---w (address)?
      |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)

      |     |        |           |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix

      |     |        |     +---w action* [order]
      |     |        |        +---w order                  int32
      |     |        |        +---w (action)?
      |     |        |           +--:(output-action-case)

      |     |        |           |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |     |        |           |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |     |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w controller-action
      |     |        |           |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |     |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
      |     |        |           |  +---w set-field
      |     |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |     |        |           |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |     |        |           |     +---w metadata
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |     |        |           |     +---w tunnel
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |     |        |           |     +---w ethernet-match
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ethernet-type!

      |     |        |           |     +---w vlan-match
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |     |        |           |     +---w ip-match
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |     |        |           |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label

      |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!

      |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |     |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |     |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8

      |     |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |     |        |           |     +---w protocol-match-fields

      |     |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |     |        |           |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8

      |     |        |           |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32

      |     |        |           |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |     |        |           |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |     |        |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

      |     |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)

      |     |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)

      |     |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)

      |     |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

      |     |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

      |     |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |     |        |              +---w sw-path-action
      |     |        +--:(clear-actions-case)

      |     |        |     +---w action* [order]
      |     |        |        +---w order                  int32
      |     |        |        +---w (action)?

      |     |        |           |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id

      |     |        |           |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64

      |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)

      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |     |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |     |        |           |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |     |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |     |        |           |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

      |     |        |           |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

      |     |        |           |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number

   |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |  |        |        +--ro (action)?

   |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |        |           |     +--ro metadata
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!

   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |        |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |        |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)

   |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |        |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)

   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
   |  |        |  +--ro apply-actions
   |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro controller-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |        |           |     +--ro metadata
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8

   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix

   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!

   |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number

   |  |        |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
   |  |        |           +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro drop-action
   |  |        |           +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro flood-action

   |  |        |           +--:(loopback-action-case)

   |  |        |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
   |  |        |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |        |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
   |  |        |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32

   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  |        +--:(apply-actions-case)
   |  |        |  +--ro apply-actions
   |  |        |     +--ro action* [order]
   |  |        |        +--ro order                  int32
   |  |        |        +--ro (action)?
   |  |        |           +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro output-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
   |  |        |           +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro controller-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
   |  |        |           +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-field
   |  |        |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |        |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |        |           |     +--ro metadata
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |        |           |     +--ro tunnel
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |        |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-match
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |        |           |     +--ro ip-match
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address

   |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label

   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |        |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8

   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |        |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |        |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields

   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)

   |  |        |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
   |  |        |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
   |  |        |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
   |  |        |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
   |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |        |           +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro group-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro group?      string
   |  |        |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
   |  |        |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |        |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro (address)?
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |        |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |        |           |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |        |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |        |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |        |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |        |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |        |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |        |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
   |  |        |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |        |              +--ro sw-path-action
   |  |        +--:(meter-case)
   |  |           +--ro meter
   |  |              +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
   |  +--ro priority?          uint16
   |  +--ro idle-timeout?      uint16
   |  +--ro hard-timeout?      uint16
   |  +--ro cookie?            flow-cookie
   |  +--ro table_id?          uint8
   |  +--ro container-name?    string
   |  +--ro cookie_mask?       flow-cookie
   |  +--ro buffer_id?         uint32
   |  +--ro out_port?          uint64
   |  +--ro out_group?         uint32
   |  +--ro flags?             flow-mod-flags
   |  +--ro flow-name?         string
   |  +--ro installHw?         boolean
   |  +--ro barrier?           boolean
   |  +--ro strict?            boolean
   |  +--ro transaction-id?    transaction-id
   +---n switch-flow-removed                     
   |  +--ro node?             inv:node-ref
   |  +--ro flow-table?       flow-table-ref
   |  +--ro priority?         uint16
   |  +--ro idle-timeout?     uint16
   |  +--ro hard-timeout?     uint16
   |  +--ro cookie?           flow-cookie
   |  +--ro table_id?         uint8
   |  +--ro removed_reason?   removed_reason_flags
   |  +--ro duration_nsec?    uint32
   |  +--ro duration_sec?     uint32
   |  +--ro packet_count?     uint64
   |  +--ro byte_count?       uint64
   |  +--ro match
   |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |     +--ro metadata
   |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
   |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
   |     +--ro tunnel
   |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
   |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |     +--ro ethernet-match
   |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
   |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
   |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
   |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
   |     +--ro vlan-match
   |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
   |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |     +--ro ip-match
   |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
   |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
   |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
   |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
   |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
   |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
   |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
   |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
   |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
   |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
   |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
   |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |     +--ro icmpv4-match
   |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |     +--ro icmpv6-match
   |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
   |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
   |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
   |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
   |     |  +--ro pbb
   |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
   |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
   |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
   |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
   +---n node-error-notification                 
   |  +--ro type?              error-type
   |  +--ro code?              uint16
   |  +--ro data?              string
   |  +--ro transaction-id?    transaction-id
   |  +--ro transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  +--ro (object-reference)?
   |  |  +--:(flow-ref)
   |  |  |  +--ro flow-ref?          types:flow-ref
   |  |  +--:(group-ref)
   |  |  |  +--ro group-ref?         group-type:group-ref
   |  |  +--:(meter-ref)
   |  |     +--ro meter-ref?         meter-type:meter-ref
   |  +--ro node?              inv:node-ref
   +---n node-experimenter-error-notification    
      +--ro type?              error-type
      +--ro exp-type?          uint16
      +--ro experimenter-id?   uint32
      +--ro data?              string
      +--ro transaction-id?    transaction-id
module: sal-group
rpcs:
   +---x add-group       
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  |  +---w group-ref?         group-type:group-ref

   |  |           +---w (action)?

   |  |              |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |              |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |              +--:(controller-action-case)

   |  |              |     +---w max-length?   uint16

   |  |              |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id

   |  |              |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64

   |  |              |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |              |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-source!

   |  |              |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address

   |  |                 +---w sw-path-action
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x remove-group    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
   |  |  +---w group-ref?         group-type:group-ref
   |  |  +---w node?              node-ref
   |  |  +---w group-type?        group-types
   |  |  +---w group-id?          group-id
   |  |  +---w group-name?        string
   |  |  +---w container-name?    string
   |  |  +---w barrier?           boolean
   |  |  +---w buckets
   |  |     +---w bucket* [bucket-id]
   |  |        +---w bucket-id      bucket-id
   |  |        +---w weight?        uint16
   |  |        +---w watch_port?    uint32
   |  |        +---w watch_group?   uint32
   |  |        +---w action* [order]
   |  |           +---w order                  int32
   |  |           +---w (action)?
   |  |              +--:(output-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w output-action
   |  |              |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
   |  |              |     +---w max-length?              uint16
   |  |              +--:(controller-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w controller-action
   |  |              |     +---w max-length?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(set-field-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-field
   |  |              |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
   |  |              |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
   |  |              |     +---w metadata
   |  |              |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
   |  |              |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
   |  |              |     +---w tunnel
   |  |              |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
   |  |              |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
   |  |              |     +---w ethernet-match
   |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
   |  |              |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
   |  |              |     +---w vlan-match
   |  |              |     |  +---w vlan-id!
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
   |  |              |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |              |     +---w ip-match
   |  |              |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
   |  |              |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
   |  |              |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
   |  |              |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
   |  |              |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
   |  |              |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
   |  |              |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
   |  |              |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
   |  |              |     |  +--:(arp-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
   |  |              |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
   |  |              |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
   |  |              |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
   |  |              |     |  +--:(udp-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
   |  |              |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
   |  |              |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
   |  |              |     +---w icmpv4-match
   |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
   |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
   |  |              |     +---w icmpv6-match
   |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
   |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
   |  |              |     +---w protocol-match-fields
   |  |              |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
   |  |              |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
   |  |              |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
   |  |              |     |  +---w pbb
   |  |              |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
   |  |              |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
   |  |              |     +---w tcp-flag-match
   |  |              |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(set-queue-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-queue-action
   |  |              |     +---w queue?      string
   |  |              |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
   |  |              +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w pop-mpls-action
   |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
   |  |              |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
   |  |              |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
   |  |              +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w push-pbb-action
   |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w pop-pbb-action
   |  |              +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w push-mpls-action
   |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
   |  |              |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
   |  |              +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
   |  |              |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
   |  |              +--:(drop-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w drop-action
   |  |              +--:(flood-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w flood-action
   |  |              +--:(flood-all-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w flood-all-action
   |  |              +--:(hw-path-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w hw-path-action
   |  |              +--:(loopback-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w loopback-action
   |  |              +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w pop-vlan-action
   |  |              +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w push-vlan-action
   |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
   |  |              |     +---w tag?             int32
   |  |              |     +---w pcp?             int32
   |  |              |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
   |  |              |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
   |  |              +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
   |  |              |  +---w copy-ttl-out
   |  |              +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
   |  |              |  +---w copy-ttl-in
   |  |              +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
   |  |              |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |              +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-dl-src-action
   |  |              |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
   |  |              +--:(group-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w group-action
   |  |              |     +---w group?      string
   |  |              |     +---w group-id?   uint32
   |  |              +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-dl-type-action
   |  |              |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
   |  |              +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-next-hop-action
   |  |              |     +---w (address)?
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |              |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |              |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
   |  |              |     +---w (address)?
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |              |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |              |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-nw-src-action
   |  |              |     +---w (address)?
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
   |  |              |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
   |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
   |  |              |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
   |  |              +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
   |  |              |     +---w tos?   int32
   |  |              +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
   |  |              |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |              +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-tp-src-action
   |  |              |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
   |  |              +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
   |  |              |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
   |  |              +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
   |  |              |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
   |  |              +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
   |  |              |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
   |  |              +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
   |  |              |  +---w strip-vlan-action
   |  |              +--:(sw-path-action-case)
   |  |                 +---w sw-path-action
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro transaction-id?   transaction-id
   +---x update-group    
      +---w input     
      |  +---w transaction-uri?   inet:uri
      |  +---w group-ref?         group-type:group-ref
      |  +---w node?              node-ref
      |  +---w original-group
      |  |  +---w group-type?       group-types
      |  |  +---w group-id?         group-id
      |  |  +---w group-name?       string
      |  |  +---w container-name?   string
      |  |  +---w barrier?          boolean
      |  |  +---w buckets
      |  |     +---w bucket* [bucket-id]
      |  |        +---w bucket-id      bucket-id
      |  |        +---w weight?        uint16
      |  |        +---w watch_port?    uint32
      |  |        +---w watch_group?   uint32
      |  |        +---w action* [order]
      |  |           +---w order                  int32
      |  |           +---w (action)?
      |  |              +--:(output-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w output-action
      |  |              |     +---w output-node-connector?   inet:uri
      |  |              |     +---w max-length?              uint16
      |  |              +--:(controller-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w controller-action
      |  |              |     +---w max-length?   uint16
      |  |              +--:(set-field-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-field
      |  |              |     +---w in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |     +---w in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
      |  |              |     +---w metadata
      |  |              |     |  +---w metadata?        uint64
      |  |              |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |     +---w tunnel
      |  |              |     |  +---w tunnel-id?     uint64
      |  |              |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |  |              |     +---w ethernet-match
      |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |  |              |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |  |              |     +---w vlan-match
      |  |              |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              |     +---w ip-match
      |  |              |     |  +---w ip-protocol?   uint8
      |  |              |     |  +---w ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
      |  |              |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |  |              |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |  |              |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |  |              |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-label
      |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w ipv6-ext-header
      |  |              |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
      |  |              |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
      |  |              |     |  +--:(arp-match)
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-op?                         uint16
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-source-hardware-address!
      |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |  |              |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |  |              |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
      |  |              |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |     +---w (layer-4-match)?
      |  |              |     |  +--:(udp-match)
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |  |              |     |  |  +---w tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
      |  |              |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
      |  |              |     |     +---w sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
      |  |              |     |     +---w sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
      |  |              |     +---w icmpv4-match
      |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv4-type?   uint8
      |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv4-code?   uint8
      |  |              |     +---w icmpv6-match
      |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv6-type?   uint8
      |  |              |     |  +---w icmpv6-code?   uint8
      |  |              |     +---w protocol-match-fields
      |  |              |     |  +---w mpls-label?   uint32
      |  |              |     |  +---w mpls-tc?      uint8
      |  |              |     |  +---w mpls-bos?     uint8
      |  |              |     |  +---w pbb
      |  |              |     |     +---w pbb-isid?   uint32
      |  |              |     |     +---w pbb-mask?   uint32
      |  |              |     +---w tcp-flag-match
      |  |              |        +---w tcp-flag?   uint16
      |  |              +--:(set-queue-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-queue-action
      |  |              |     +---w queue?      string
      |  |              |     +---w queue-id?   uint32
      |  |              +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w pop-mpls-action
      |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |              +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-mpls-ttl-action
      |  |              |     +---w mpls-ttl?   uint8
      |  |              +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-nw-ttl-action
      |  |              |     +---w nw-ttl?   uint8
      |  |              +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w push-pbb-action
      |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |              +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w pop-pbb-action
      |  |              +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w push-mpls-action
      |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |              +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
      |  |              |  +---w dec-mpls-ttl
      |  |              +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
      |  |              |  +---w dec-nw-ttl
      |  |              +--:(drop-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w drop-action
      |  |              +--:(flood-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w flood-action
      |  |              +--:(flood-all-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w flood-all-action
      |  |              +--:(hw-path-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w hw-path-action
      |  |              +--:(loopback-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w loopback-action
      |  |              +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w pop-vlan-action
      |  |              +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w push-vlan-action
      |  |              |     +---w ethernet-type?   uint16
      |  |              |     +---w tag?             int32
      |  |              |     +---w pcp?             int32
      |  |              |     +---w cfi?             vlan-cfi
      |  |              |     +---w vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
      |  |              |  +---w copy-ttl-out
      |  |              +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
      |  |              |  +---w copy-ttl-in
      |  |              +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-dl-dst-action
      |  |              |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
      |  |              +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-dl-src-action
      |  |              |     +---w address?   yang:mac-address
      |  |              +--:(group-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w group-action
      |  |              |     +---w group?      string
      |  |              |     +---w group-id?   uint32
      |  |              +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-dl-type-action
      |  |              |     +---w dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
      |  |              +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-next-hop-action
      |  |              |     +---w (address)?
      |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |              |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |              |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-nw-dst-action
      |  |              |     +---w (address)?
      |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |              |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |              |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-nw-src-action
      |  |              |     +---w (address)?
      |  |              |        +--:(ipv4)
      |  |              |        |  +---w ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
      |  |              |        +--:(ipv6)
      |  |              |           +---w ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
      |  |              +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-nw-tos-action
      |  |              |     +---w tos?   int32
      |  |              +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-tp-dst-action
      |  |              |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |              +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-tp-src-action
      |  |              |     +---w port?   inet:port-number
      |  |              +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-vlan-cfi-action
      |  |              |     +---w vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
      |  |              +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-vlan-id-action
      |  |              |     +---w vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
      |  |              +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w set-vlan-pcp-action
      |  |              |     +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
      |  |              +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
      |  |              |  +---w strip-vlan-action
      |  |              +--:(sw-path-action-case)
      |  |                 +---w sw-path-action
      |  +---w updated-group
      |     +---w group-type?       group-types
      |     +---w group-id?         group-id
      |     +---w group-name?       string
      |     +---w container-name?   string

      |     +---w buckets
      |        +---w bucket* [bucket-id]

      |                 |     |  +---w metadata-mask?   uint64
      |                 |     +---w tunnel

      |                 |     |  +---w tunnel-mask?   uint64
      |                 |     +---w ethernet-match
      |                 |     |  +---w ethernet-source!
      |                 |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |                 |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |                 |     |  +---w ethernet-destination!
      |                 |     |  |  +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |                 |     |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |                 |     |  +---w ethernet-type!
      |                 |     |     +---w type    l2t:ether-type
      |                 |     +---w vlan-match
      |                 |     |  +---w vlan-id!
      |                 |     |  |  +---w vlan-id-present?   boolean
      |                 |     |  |  +---w vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
      |                 |     |  +---w vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

      |                 |     |  +---w ip-ecn?        uint8
      |                 |     |  +---w ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
      |                 |     +---w (layer-3-match)?
      |                 |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
      |                 |     |  |  +---w ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
      |                 |     |  |  +---w ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
      |                 |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)

      |                 |     |  |  +---w ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix

      |                 |     |  |     +---w ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16

      |                 |     |  |  +---w arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

      |                 |     |  |  |  +---w mask?      yang:mac-address
      |                 |     |  |  +---w arp-target-hardware-address!
      |                 |     |  |     +---w address    yang:mac-address
      |                 |     |  |     +---w mask?      yang:mac-address

      |                 |     |     +---w tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix

      |                 |     |  |  +---w udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
      |                 |     |  |  +---w udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
