                  |           |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           |           |     +--ro ip-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8

                  |           |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
                  |           |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
                  |           |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           |           |     +--ro ip-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

                  |           |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address

                  |           |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8

                  |           |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri

                  |           |           +--:(controller-action-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro controller-action
                  |           |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
                  |           |           +--:(set-field-case)
                  |           |           |  +--ro set-field
                  |           |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |           |     +--ro metadata
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
                  |           |           |     +--ro tunnel
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |           |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

                  |           |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
                  |           |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp

                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)

                  |           |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)

                  |           |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                  |           |              +--ro sw-path-action
                  |           +--:(meter-case)
                  |              +--ro meter
                  |                 +--ro meter-id?   meter:meter-id
                  +--:(next-table)
                  |  +--ro tables
                  |     +--ro table-ids*   uint8
                  +--:(next-table-miss)
                  |  +--ro tables-miss
                  |     +--ro table-ids*   uint8
                  +--:(write-actions)
                  |  +--ro write-actions
                  |     +--ro action* [order]
                  |        +--ro order                  int32
                  |        +--ro (action)?
                  |           +--:(output-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro output-action
                  |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
                  |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
                  |           +--:(controller-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro controller-action
                  |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-field-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-field
                  |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |     +--ro metadata
                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro tunnel
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
                  |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           |     +--ro ip-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)

                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix

                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label

                  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16

                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix

                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address

                  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number

                  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number

                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8

                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8

                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
                  |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)

                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
                  |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           |     +--ro ip-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
                  |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
                  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
                  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
                  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
                  |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
                  |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro pbb
                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
                  |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
                  |           |     +--ro queue?      string
                  |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
                  |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
                  |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
                  |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
                  |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
                  |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action
                  |           +--:(push-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
                  |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl
                  |           +--:(dec-nw-ttl-case)
                  |           |  +--ro dec-nw-ttl
                  |           +--:(drop-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro drop-action
                  |           +--:(flood-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro flood-action
                  |           +--:(flood-all-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro flood-all-action
                  |           +--:(hw-path-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro hw-path-action
                  |           +--:(loopback-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro loopback-action
                  |           +--:(pop-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-vlan-action
                  |           +--:(push-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro push-vlan-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           |     +--ro tag?             int32
                  |           |     +--ro pcp?             int32
                  |           |     +--ro cfi?             vlan-cfi
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?         l2t:vlan-id
                  |           +--:(copy-ttl-out-case)
                  |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-out
                  |           +--:(copy-ttl-in-case)
                  |           |  +--ro copy-ttl-in
                  |           +--:(set-dl-dst-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-dl-dst-action
                  |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
                  |           +--:(set-dl-src-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-dl-src-action
                  |           |     +--ro address?   yang:mac-address
                  |           +--:(group-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro group-action
                  |           |     +--ro group?      string
                  |           |     +--ro group-id?   uint32
                  |           +--:(set-dl-type-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-dl-type-action
                  |           |     +--ro dl-type?   l2t:ether-type
                  |           +--:(set-next-hop-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-next-hop-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           +--:(set-nw-dst-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-dst-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           +--:(set-nw-src-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-src-action
                  |           |     +--ro (address)?
                  |           |        +--:(ipv4)
                  |           |        |  +--ro ipv4-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |        +--:(ipv6)
                  |           |           +--ro ipv6-address?   inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           +--:(set-nw-tos-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-tos-action
                  |           |     +--ro tos?   int32
                  |           +--:(set-tp-dst-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-tp-dst-action
                  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
                  |           +--:(set-tp-src-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-tp-src-action
                  |           |     +--ro port?   inet:port-number
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-cfi-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-cfi-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
                  |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                  |              +--ro sw-path-action
                  +--:(apply-actions-miss)
                  |  +--ro apply-actions-miss
                  |     +--ro action* [order]
                  |        +--ro order                  int32
                  |        +--ro (action)?
                  |           +--:(output-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro output-action
                  |           |     +--ro output-node-connector?   inet:uri
                  |           |     +--ro max-length?              uint16
                  |           +--:(controller-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro controller-action
                  |           |     +--ro max-length?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-field-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-field
                  |           |     +--ro in-port?                        inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |     +--ro in-phy-port?                    inv:node-connector-id
                  |           |     +--ro metadata
                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata?        uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro metadata-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro tunnel
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-id?     uint64
                  |           |     |  +--ro tunnel-mask?   uint64
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-source!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-destination!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--ro ethernet-type!
                  |           |     |     +--ro type    l2t:ether-type
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-id!
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id-present?   boolean
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro vlan-id?           l2t:vlan-id
                  |           |     |  +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           |     +--ro ip-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-protocol?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-dscp?       inet:dscp
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-ecn?        uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro ip-proto?      inet:ip-version
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-3-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv4-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-source?                    inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv4-destination?               inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  +--:(ipv6-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-source?                    inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-destination?               inet:ipv6-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-target?                 inet:ipv6-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-label
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro ipv6-flabel?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro flabel-mask?   inet:ipv6-flow-label
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-sll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-nd-tll?                    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro ipv6-ext-header
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr?        uint16
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro ipv6-exthdr-mask?   uint16
                  |           |     |  +--:(arp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-op?                         uint16
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-transport-address?   inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-source-hardware-address!
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  |  +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro arp-target-hardware-address!
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro address    yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  |     +--ro mask?      yang:mac-address
                  |           |     |  +--:(tunnel-ipv4-match)
                  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-source?             inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     |     +--ro tunnel-ipv4-destination?        inet:ipv4-prefix
                  |           |     +--ro (layer-4-match)?
                  |           |     |  +--:(udp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro udp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  +--:(tcp-match)
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-source-port?                inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  |  +--ro tcp-destination-port?           inet:port-number
                  |           |     |  +--:(sctp-match)
                  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-source-port?               inet:port-number
                  |           |     |     +--ro sctp-destination-port?          inet:port-number
                  |           |     +--ro icmpv4-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-type?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv4-code?   uint8
                  |           |     +--ro icmpv6-match
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-type?   uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro icmpv6-code?   uint8
                  |           |     +--ro protocol-match-fields
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-label?   uint32
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-tc?      uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro mpls-bos?     uint8
                  |           |     |  +--ro pbb
                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-isid?   uint32
                  |           |     |     +--ro pbb-mask?   uint32
                  |           |     +--ro tcp-flag-match
                  |           |        +--ro tcp-flag?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-queue-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-queue-action
                  |           |     +--ro queue?      string
                  |           |     +--ro queue-id?   uint32
                  |           +--:(pop-mpls-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-mpls-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(set-mpls-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-mpls-ttl-action
                  |           |     +--ro mpls-ttl?   uint8
                  |           +--:(set-nw-ttl-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-nw-ttl-action
                  |           |     +--ro nw-ttl?   uint8
                  |           +--:(push-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro push-pbb-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(pop-pbb-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro pop-pbb-action

                  |           |  +--ro push-mpls-action
                  |           |     +--ro ethernet-type?   uint16
                  |           +--:(dec-mpls-ttl-case)
                  |           |  +--ro dec-mpls-ttl

                  |           |     +--ro vlan-cfi?   vlan-cfi
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-id-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-id-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-id?   l2t:vlan-id
                  |           +--:(set-vlan-pcp-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro set-vlan-pcp-action
                  |           |     +--ro vlan-pcp?   l2t:vlan-pcp
                  |           +--:(strip-vlan-action-case)
                  |           |  +--ro strip-vlan-action
                  |           +--:(sw-path-action-case)
                  |              +--ro sw-path-action
                  +--:(match)
                  |  +--ro match-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(wildcards)
                  |  +--ro wildcard-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(write-setfield)
                  |  +--ro write-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(write-setfield-miss)
                  |  +--ro write-setfield-miss
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(apply-setfield)
                  |  +--ro apply-setfield
                  |     +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                  |        +--ro match-type    identityref
                  |        +--ro has-mask?     boolean
                  +--:(apply-setfield-miss)
                     +--ro apply-setfield-miss
                        +--ro set-field-match* [match-type]
                           +--ro match-type    identityref
                           +--ro has-mask?     boolean
module: shutdown-impl
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(shutdown)
      +--rw secret?   string
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:state:
   +--:(shutdown)
rpcs:
   +---x shutdown    
      +---w input     
         +---w context-instance?   instance-identifier
         +---w input-secret?       string
         +---w max-wait-time?      uint32
         +---w reason?             string
module: statistics-manager
augment /config:modules/config:module/config:configuration:
   +--:(statistics-manager)
      +--rw rpc-registry
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw notification-service
      |  +--rw type    service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw data-broker
      |  +--rw type?   service-type-ref
      |  +--rw name    -> /config:services/service[config:type=current()/../type]/instance/name
      +--rw statistics-manager-settings
         +--rw min-request-net-monitor-interval?   int32
         +--rw max-nodes-for-collector?            int32
module: stp-status-aware-node-connector
augment /inv:nodes/inv:node/inv:node-connector:
   +--rw status?   stp-status
module: system-notifications
notifications:
   +---n disconnect-event     
   |  +--ro info?   string
   +---n switch-idle-event    
      +--ro info?   string
module: tailf-aaa
   +--rw aaa
   |  +--rw authentication
   |  |  +--rw users
   |  |  |  +--rw user* [name]
   |  |  |     +--rw name          string
   |  |  |     +--rw uid           int32
   |  |  |     +--rw gid           int32
   |  |  |     +--rw password      passwdStr
   |  |  |     +--rw ssh_keydir    string
   |  |  |     +--rw homedir       string
   |  |  +--rw groups
   |  |     +--rw group* [name]
   |  |        +--rw name     string

      +--rw tagnode                dataplane-ifname

      +--rw dhcpv6-options!

      |  +--rw temporary?         empty
      +--rw ip
      |  +--rw enable-proxy-arp?     empty
      |  +--rw rpf-check?            enumeration

      +--rw mtu?                   uint32
      +--rw disable?               empty

      |  +--rw vlan?                  uint32
      |  +--rw description?           string
      |  +--rw dhcpv6-options!
      |  |  +--rw parameters-only?   empty
      |  |  +--rw temporary?         empty
      |  +--rw ip!
      |  |  +--rw enable-proxy-arp?   empty
      |  |  +--rw rpf-check?          enumeration
      |  +--rw ipv6!
      |  +--rw mtu?                   uint32
      |  +--rw disable?               empty
      |  +--rw address*               if:address-dhcp
      |  +--rw disable-link-detect?   empty
      |  +--rw bridge-group!
      |     +--rw priority?   uint32
      |     +--rw bridge?     string
      |     +--rw cost?       uint32
      +--rw sflow?                 empty
      +--rw address*               if:address-dhcp
      +--rw mac?                   types:mac-address
      +--rw disable-link-detect?   empty
      +--rw bridge-group!
         +--rw priority?     uint32
         +--rw root-block?   empty
         +--rw bpdu-guard?   empty
         +--rw bridge?       string
         +--rw cost?         uint32

module: vyatta-op
rpcs:
   +---x ping         
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w host     string
   |  |  +---w count?   uint32
   |  |  +---w ttl?     uint8
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro tx-packet-count?   uint32
   |     +--ro rx-packet-count?   uint32
   |     +--ro min-delay?         uint32
   |     +--ro average-delay?     uint32
   |     +--ro max-delay?         uint32
   +---x interface    
   |  +---w input     
   |  |  +---w name    string
   |  +--ro output    
   |     +--ro address* [ip]
   |     |  +--ro ip    types:ip-prefix
   |     +--ro admin-status?   enumeration
   |     +--ro oper-status?    enumeration
   |     +--ro description?    string
   +---x route        
      +---w input     
      |  +---w family?        enumeration
      |  +---w destination?   destination
      +--ro output    
         +--ro route* [destination]
            +--ro destination    destination
            +--ro source?        types:ip-address
            +--ro path* [entry]
               +--ro entry       uint64
               +--ro device?     string
               +--ro next-hop?   types:ip-address

module: vyatta-policy-qos
augment /policy:policy:
   +--rw qos* [tagnode]
      +--rw tagnode    name
      +--rw shaper
         +--rw vlan* [tagnode]
         |  +--rw tagnode          uint16
         |  +--rw description?     string
         |  +--rw bandwidth?       union
         |  +--rw default?         name
         |  +--rw burst?           burst-size
         |  +--rw period?          uint32
         |  +--rw traffic-class* [tagnode]
         |  |  +--rw tagnode        uint32
         |  |  +--rw description?   string
         |  |  +--rw bandwidth?     union
         |  |  +--rw burst?         burst-size
         |  +--rw class* [tagnode]
         |     +--rw tagnode        uint32
         |     +--rw description?   string
         |     +--rw profile?       name
         |     +--rw match* [tagnode]
         |        +--rw tagnode        name
         |        +--rw tcp!
         |        |  +--rw flags?   string
         |        +--rw description?   string
         |        +--rw action?        enumeration
         |        +--rw pcp?           uint32
         |        +--rw mark
         |        |  +--rw pcp?    uint32
         |        |  +--rw dscp?   dscp:dscp-name-or-value
         |        +--rw police
         |        |  +--rw bandwidth?   bandwidth-suffix
         |        |  +--rw burst?       burst-size
         |        |  +--rw then
         |        |     +--rw action?   enumeration
         |        |     +--rw mark
         |        |        +--rw pcp?    uint32
         |        |        +--rw dscp?   dscp:dscp-name-or-value
         |        +--rw fragment?      empty
         |        +--rw source!

         |        +--rw log?           empty
         |        +--rw destination!

         |        |  +--rw address?       string
         |        |  +--rw port?          string
         |        +--rw dscp?          dscp:dscp-name-or-value
         |        +--rw protocol?      string
         +--rw description?      string

         |  +--rw tagnode          name
         |  +--rw period?          uint32

         |  +--rw burst?           burst-size
         |  +--rw bandwidth?       bandwidth-suffix
         |  +--rw map

         |  |  |  +--rw to?        uint32

         |  |     +--rw to?        uint32

         |  |  +--rw weight?          uint8
         |  +--rw traffic-class* [tagnode]

         |     +--rw description?   string
         |     +--rw bandwidth?     union
         |     +--rw burst?         burst-size
         +--rw traffic-class* [tagnode]
         |  +--rw tagnode          uint32
         |  +--rw description?     string
         |  +--rw bandwidth?       union
         |  +--rw burst?           burst-size
         |  +--rw queue-limit?     uint16
         |  +--rw random-detect!

         |     +--rw max-threshold?      uint16
         |     +--rw filter-weight?      uint16
         |     +--rw mark-probability?   uint16

         +--rw burst?            burst-size
         +--rw period?           uint32

            +--rw tagnode        uint32

            +--rw match* [tagnode]
               +--rw tagnode        name
               +--rw tcp!

               +--rw description?   string

               +--rw pcp?           uint32
               +--rw mark
               |  +--rw pcp?    uint32

               |  +--rw bandwidth?   bandwidth-suffix
               |  +--rw burst?       burst-size
               |  +--rw then
               |     +--rw action?   enumeration
               |     +--rw mark
               |        +--rw pcp?    uint32
               |        +--rw dscp?   dscp:dscp-name-or-value

               +--rw source!

               |  +--rw address?       string
